UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Jitters\' Growling Gut',details_loc9='I\'ve been stuck hiding in this ghost town for weeks, and I haven\'t eaten anything but grubs and weeds!  I need some decent food, and I\'m willing to trade well for it.$b$bBring me a feast and I\'ll pay you handsomely.$b$bI heard Chef Grual at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire makes very good Dusky Crab Cakes...' WHERE entry=5; /* title: Jitters\' Growling Gut */ /* details: I\'ve been stuck hiding in this ghost town for weeks, and I haven\'t eaten anything but grubs and weeds!  I need some decent food, and I\'m willing to trade well for it.$B$BBring me a feast and I\'ll pay you handsomely.$B$BI heard Chef Grual at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire makes very good Dusky Crab Cakes... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Bounty on Garrick Padfoot',details_loc9='Garrick Padfoot - a cutthroat who\'s plagued our farmers and merchants for weeks - was seen at a shack near the vineyards, which lies east of the Abbey and across the bridge.  Bring me the villain\'s head, and earn his bounty!$b$bBut be wary, $n.  Garrick has gathered a gang of thugs around him.  He will not be an easy man to reach.' WHERE entry=6; /* title: Bounty on Garrick Padfoot */ /* details: Garrick Padfoot - a cutthroat who\'s plagued our farmers and merchants for weeks - was seen at a shack near the vineyards, which lies east of the Abbey and across the bridge.  Bring me the villain\'s head, and earn his bounty!$B$BBut be wary, $N.  Garrick has gathered a gang of thugs around him.  He will not be an easy man to reach. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Rogue\'s Deal',details_loc9='Hey, mate! Do a favor for a young man who\'s been fighting more than his fair share of mindless zombies and spiders?$b$bI got this here letter that needs to go to Brill... to an innkeeper named Renee something-or-other. Don\'t really matter none what her last name is.$b$bAnyway, it\'s a nice cozy little place full of victims of the plague trying to make their way in the world. And it be a great spot for you to rest too if the need arises. You should check it out... you do and I\'ll pay you well.' WHERE entry=8; /* title: A Rogue\'s Deal */ /* details: Hey, mate! Do a favor for a young man who\'s been fighting more than his fair share of mindless zombies and spiders?$B$BI got this here letter that needs to go to Brill... to an innkeeper named Renee something-or-other. Don\'t really matter none what her last name is.$B$BAnyway, it\'s a nice cozy little place full of victims of the plague trying to make their way in the world. And it be a great spot for you to rest too if the need arises. You should check it out... you do and I\'ll pay you well. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Killing Fields',details_loc9='Look at what has happened to this place!  These lands were once occupied by good farm folk.  But the damned thieves have driven them all off.  Not me, though!  But it seems some Harvest Watchers have taken over the fields.$b$bIf you\'re up for the work, I\'d like you to go out and kill twenty of them.  Come back when you\'re done for your pay.  If you finish up with the ones in my field, clear them from the neighboring fields as well.' WHERE entry=9; /* title: The Killing Fields */ /* details: Look at what has happened to this place!  These lands were once occupied by good farm folk.  But the damned thieves have driven them all off.  Not me, though!  But it seems some Harvest Watchers have taken over the fields.$B$BIf you\'re up for the work, I\'d like you to go out and kill twenty of them.  Come back when you\'re done for your pay.  If you finish up with the ones in my field, clear them from the neighboring fields as well. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Scrimshank Redemption',details_loc9='Oh, this is just terrible!  I sent out my top assistant, Junior Surveyor Scrimshank, into the desert southeast of here.  That\'s an area we call the Gaping Chasm.  Well, he\'s gone missing, and his last report had more of those weird bugs where he was.  Could it be that they\'ve infested two major regions of the desert now?$b$bI need you to head into the Gaping Chasm and look for Scrimshank, please!  That... or at least find his surveying equipment.  I fear that may be all that is left of the poor sod.' WHERE entry=10; /* title: The Scrimshank Redemption */ /* details: Oh, this is just terrible!  I sent out my top assistant, Junior Surveyor Scrimshank, into the desert southeast of here.  That\'s an area we call the Gaping Chasm.  Well, he\'s gone missing, and his last report had more of those weird bugs where he was.  Could it be that they\'ve infested two major regions of the desert now?$B$BI need you to head into the Gaping Chasm and look for Scrimshank, please!  That... or at least find his surveying equipment.  I fear that may be all that is left of the poor sod. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Taglia sugli Gnoll Zampaumida',details_loc9='Gli Gnoll, delle creature selvagge che non dovrebbero abitare queste terre, sono stati avvistati lungo i confini della Foresta di Elwynn. Un grosso branco, composto da un numero di esemplari che non possiamo affrontare da soli, ha invaso i boschi a sud della torre di guardia. Un altro gruppo ha infestato le zone vicino al Lago del Memoriale a est.$b$bL\'Esercito di Roccavento ricompenserà chiunque dia una mano a eliminarli. Portami le Polsiere degli Gnoll Dipinte come prova della loro uccisione.',objectives_loc9='Porta 8 Polsiere degli Gnoll Dipinte al Vicesceriffo Rainer nella Caserma.' WHERE entry=11; /* title: Riverpaw Gnoll Bounty */ /* details: Gnolls, brutish creatures with no decent business in these lands, have been seen along the borders of Elwynn Forest.  A large pack of them, many more than we can handle alone, have infested the woods south of the guard tower yonder.  Another group has infested the areas near Stone Cairn Lake to the east.$B$BThe Stormwind Army will commend whomever helps kill them.  Bring me their painted gnoll armbands as proof of your deed. */ /* objectives: Bring 8 Painted Gnoll Armbands to Deputy Rainer at the Barracks. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Milizia Popolare',details_loc9='The People\'s Militia has but one goal:  To defend the lands of Westfall and return peace to our surroundings.  Unfortunately, the price of peace is often blood. $b$bOne of my scouts has brought word of a band of Defias Trappers wreaking havoc nearby.  I have reports of Defias Trapper sightings near the Jangolode Mine to the Northwest as well as at the Molsen Farm and Furlbrow\'s Pumpkin Farm. If you seek to join our ranks, slay 15 Defias Trappers and 15 Defias Smugglers then return to me.' WHERE entry=12; /* title: The People\'s Militia */ /* details: The People\'s Militia has but one goal:  To defend the lands of Westfall and return peace to our surroundings.  Unfortunately, the price of peace is often blood. $B$BOne of my scouts has brought word of a band of Defias Trappers wreaking havoc nearby.  I have reports of Defias Trapper sightings near the Jangolode Mine to the Northwest as well as at the Molsen Farm and Furlbrow\'s Pumpkin Farm. If you seek to join our ranks, slay 15 Defias Trappers and 15 Defias Smugglers then return to me. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Milizia Popolare',details_loc9='A band of vicious Defias Pillagers has been seen plundering the Gold Coast Quarry, Moonbrook and the Alexston Farmstead.  The People\'s Militia will not stand for such behavior.  Dispatch immediately, $n, and make the Light\'s presence known in Westfall.$b$bThe Gold Coast Quarry is near the shore, to the West of the tower.  As the next step of your training, I want you to kill 15 of those foul Defias Pillagers and 15 Defias Looters.' WHERE entry=13; /* title: The People\'s Militia */ /* details: A band of vicious Defias Pillagers has been seen plundering the Gold Coast Quarry, Moonbrook and the Alexston Farmstead.  The People\'s Militia will not stand for such behavior.  Dispatch immediately, $n, and make the Light\'s presence known in Westfall.$B$BThe Gold Coast Quarry is near the shore, to the West of the tower.  As the next step of your training, I want you to kill 15 of those foul Defias Pillagers and 15 Defias Looters. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Milizia Popolare',details_loc9='Some Defias have eluded us.  My most trusted scout reports that these Defias have been looting and pillaging the countryside, all the way into Southern Westfall.  We believe they are hiding out in the Dagger Hills, plotting their next move.   Slay the wretches in the name of The People\'s Militia.' WHERE entry=14; /* title: The People\'s Militia */ /* details: Some Defias have eluded us.  My most trusted scout reports that these Defias have been looting and pillaging the countryside, all the way into Southern Westfall.  We believe they are hiding out in the Dagger Hills, plotting their next move.   Slay the wretches in the name of The People\'s Militia. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Dissetare Gerard' WHERE entry=16; /* title: Give Gerard a Drink */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Uldaman Reagent Run',details_loc9='I\'ve heard about a newly discovered plant called the magenta fungus caps.  They grow in clusters at the Uldaman dig site and can be found in the early tunnels and deep within the less-explored areas.  I want to study their potential use in alchemy, and that\'s where you come in.$b$bFind the magenta cap clusters and bring me a dozen caps.  Be warned, the clusters may spew out poison spores if jostled.$b$bDo this for me, and I\'ll whip up a batch of one of my famous restorative elixirs for you!' WHERE entry=17; /* title: Uldaman Reagent Run */ /* details: I\'ve heard about a newly discovered plant called the magenta fungus caps.  They grow in clusters at the Uldaman dig site and can be found in the early tunnels and deep within the less-explored areas.  I want to study their potential use in alchemy, and that\'s where you come in.$B$BFind the magenta cap clusters and bring me a dozen caps.  Be warned, the clusters may spew out poison spores if jostled.$B$BDo this for me, and I\'ll whip up a batch of one of my famous restorative elixirs for you! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Brotherhood of Thieves',details_loc9='Recently, a new group of thieves has been hanging around Northshire.  They call themselves the Defias Brotherhood, and have been seen across the river to the east.$b$bI don\'t know what they\'re up to, but I\'m sure it\'s not good!  Bring me the bandanas they wear, and I\'ll reward you with a weapon.' WHERE entry=18; /* title: Brotherhood of Thieves */ /* details: Recently, a new group of thieves has been hanging around Northshire.  They call themselves the Defias Brotherhood, and have been seen across the river to the east.$B$BI don\'t know what they\'re up to, but I\'m sure it\'s not good!  Bring me the bandanas they wear, and I\'ll reward you with a weapon. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Tharil\'zun',details_loc9='Blackrock Outrunners and Renegades are running ambushes between here and Stonewatch Keep.  The leader of the Outrunners is an orc named Tharil\'zun--we want this orc.  Bring me the head of Tharil\'zun!' WHERE entry=19; /* title: Tharil\'zun */ /* details: Blackrock Outrunners and Renegades are running ambushes between here and Stonewatch Keep.  The leader of the Outrunners is an orc named Tharil\'zun--we want this orc.  Bring me the head of Tharil\'zun! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Blackrock Menace',details_loc9='The Blackrock orcs have travelled from the Burning Steppes and claimed Stonewatch Keep to the north.  From there they maraud the areas north of Lakeshire and keep its citizens in town, penned like cattle.$b$bHelp rid Lakeshire of this menace.  Kill these Blackrock orcs and bring me ten of their Battleworn Axes as proof.$b$bAnd although Blackrocks threaten us from the north, we\'ve received reports of more in the southeastern pocket of Redridge.  If you find any there, then they too should be hunted.' WHERE entry=20; /* title: Blackrock Menace */ /* details: The Blackrock orcs have travelled from the Burning Steppes and claimed Stonewatch Keep to the north.  From there they maraud the areas north of Lakeshire and keep its citizens in town, penned like cattle.$B$BHelp rid Lakeshire of this menace.  Kill these Blackrock orcs and bring me ten of their Battleworn Axes as proof.$B$BAnd although Blackrocks threaten us from the north, we\'ve received reports of more in the southeastern pocket of Redridge.  If you find any there, then they too should be hunted. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Torta di Fegato di Goretusk',details_loc9='The onions are peeled.  The garlic is minced.  The rosemary is crushed.  The crust has been baked.  The dill weed is chopped.  The gravy is simmering.  Now all I need for my famous meat pie are 8 Goretusk Livers!' WHERE entry=22; /* title: Goretusk Liver Pie */ /* details: The onions are peeled.  The garlic is minced.  The rosemary is crushed.  The crust has been baked.  The dill weed is chopped.  The gravy is simmering.  Now all I need for my famous meat pie are 8 Goretusk Livers! */
