UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Trial of the Lake',details_loc9='[For your first trial, search the depths of Lake Elune\'ara to locate a Shrine Bauble.  It decays rapidly, so proceed with it to the Shrine of Remulos post haste.  Use the bauble at the shrine, and then speak with Tajarri there; she is one of Moonglade\'s most trusted wardens.$b$bYou only have a set amount of time to complete the task, and you may be competing against other druids searching for baubles themselves.  Mental and physical dexterity will be critical to your success.$b$bGood luck, $n.]' WHERE entry=28; /* title: Trial of the Lake */ /* details: For your first trial, search the depths of Lake Elune\'ara to locate a Shrine Bauble.  It decays rapidly, so proceed with it to the Shrine of Remulos post haste.  Use the bauble at the shrine, and then speak with Tajarri there; she is one of Moonglade\'s most trusted wardens.$B$BYou only have a set amount of time to complete the task, and you may be competing against other druids searching for baubles themselves.  Mental and physical dexterity will be critical to your success.$B$BGood luck, $N. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Trial of the Lake',details_loc9='[For your first trial, search the depths of Lake Elune\'ara to locate a Shrine Bauble.  It decays rapidly, so proceed with it to the Shrine of Remulos post haste.  Use the bauble at the shrine, and then speak with Tajarri there; she is one of Moonglade\'s most trusted wardens.$b$bYou only have a set amount of time to complete the task, and you may be competing against other druids searching for baubles themselves.  Mental and physical dexterity will be critical to your success.$b$bGood luck, $n.]' WHERE entry=29; /* title: Trial of the Lake */ /* details: For your first trial, search the depths of Lake Elune\'ara to locate a Shrine Bauble.  It decays rapidly, so proceed with it to the Shrine of Remulos post haste.  Use the bauble at the shrine, and then speak with Tajarri there; she is one of Moonglade\'s most trusted wardens.$B$BYou only have a set amount of time to complete the task, and you may be competing against other druids searching for baubles themselves.  Mental and physical dexterity will be critical to your success.$B$BGood luck, $N. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Trial of the Sea Lion',details_loc9='For the second trial, you\'ll need the two halves that make the Pendant of the Sea Lion.  One half draws power from the agility of the sea lion aspect, gliding through water; the other draws power from the incredible endurance of the sea lion aspect.  Druids draw on both these traits equally to embody the aspect of their aquatic form.$b$bSpeak with the locals of Moonglade to learn where the parts may lie, and bring both here to join them together.  Once formed, take the pendant to Dendrite Starblaze.' WHERE entry=30; /* title: Trial of the Sea Lion */ /* details: For the second trial, you\'ll need the two halves that make the Pendant of the Sea Lion.  One half draws power from the agility of the sea lion aspect, gliding through water; the other draws power from the incredible endurance of the sea lion aspect.  Druids draw on both these traits equally to embody the aspect of their aquatic form.$B$BSpeak with the locals of Moonglade to learn where the parts may lie, and bring both here to join them together.  Once formed, take the pendant to Dendrite Starblaze. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Forma Acquatica',details_loc9='[You have completed the necessary lessons all young druids are taught before they can adopt an aquatic aspect.  Go now back to your trainer, Turak Runetotem, in Thunder Bluff.  Show him your pendant and prove to him you are ready to learn what he has to teach you.  He will complete your training, allowing you to become one with the water.$b$bGoodbye, young druid.  We shall speak again.]' WHERE entry=31; /* title: Aquatic Form */ /* details: You have completed the necessary lessons all young druids are taught before they can adopt an aquatic aspect.  Go now back to your trainer, Turak Runetotem, in Thunder Bluff.  Show him your pendant and prove to him you are ready to learn what he has to teach you.  He will complete your training, allowing you to become one with the water.$B$BGoodbye, young druid.  We shall speak again. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rise of the Silithid',details_loc9='Here\'s your report.  I urge you to take it to someone who might have working knowledge in this kind of thing.$b$bI know this troll scholar named Zilzibin Drumlore.  He\'s spent a lot of time studying life forms that are unique to the ecology of Azeroth; he\'s a historian to boot!  If you want someone to help figure out what exactly this threat is and how to stop it, give this report to him.  We\'re going to need all the help we can get.$b$bZil lives in a house on the second tier of the Drag in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=32; /* title: Rise of the Silithid */ /* details: Here\'s your report.  I urge you to take it to someone who might have working knowledge in this kind of thing.$B$BI know this troll scholar named Zilzibin Drumlore.  He\'s spent a lot of time studying life forms that are unique to the ecology of Azeroth; he\'s a historian to boot!  If you want someone to help figure out what exactly this threat is and how to stop it, give this report to him.  We\'re going to need all the help we can get.$B$BZil lives in a house on the second tier of the Drag in Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='An Unwelcome Guest',details_loc9='Once again my garden was trampled and pillaged.  And I know the brute who is doing it.  It\'s that forsaken boar, the one Marshal Marris has taken to calling Bellygrub.$b$bI won\'t be able to re-plant the daffodils until next season now.  Ruined!  All ruined by that one menacing boar.  Put an end to that pest!  Show me his tusk and I\'d be happy to reward you.  He seems to spend his time foraging in the field southwest of Lakeshire but occasionally he roams over here and into my garden.' WHERE entry=34; /* title: An Unwelcome Guest */ /* details: Once again my garden was trampled and pillaged.  And I know the brute who is doing it.  It\'s that forsaken boar, the one Marshal Marris has taken to calling Bellygrub.$B$BI won\'t be able to re-plant the daffodils until next season now.  Ruined!  All ruined by that one menacing boar.  Put an end to that pest!  Show me his tusk and I\'d be happy to reward you.  He seems to spend his time foraging in the field southwest of Lakeshire but occasionally he roams over here and into my garden. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Altre preoccupazioni',objectives_loc9='Il Maresciallo Dughan ti ha chiesto di parlare con la Guardia Thomas.' WHERE entry=35; /* title: Further Concerns */ /* objectives: Marshal Dughan wants you to speak with Guard Thomas. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Sufato di Westfall',details_loc9='I never thought the day would come when I\'d leave the farm.  But the fields are overrun with thieves and it\'s far too dangerous for us here now.  As soon as Farmer Furlbrow gets the wagon fixed, we\'ll be on our way.  $b $bMaybe you could do me a favor?  Let me scribble down my recipe for Westfall stew.  Please take it to Salma Saldean over on the farm yonder.  The Saldean\'s farm is just beyond the fork in the road.' WHERE entry=36; /* title: Westfall Stew */ /* details: I never thought the day would come when I\'d leave the farm.  But the fields are overrun with thieves and it\'s far too dangerous for us here now.  As soon as Farmer Furlbrow gets the wagon fixed, we\'ll be on our way.  $B $BMaybe you could do me a favor?  Let me scribble down my recipe for Westfall stew.  Please take it to Salma Saldean over on the farm yonder.  The Saldean\'s farm is just beyond the fork in the road. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Le guardie scomparse',details_loc9='Pochi giorni fa abbiamo inviato due guardie, Rolf e Malakai, in perlustrazione lungo il fiume. Non sono ancora tornate. Per completare il mio rapporto devo sapere che fine hanno fatto.$b$bRisali il fiume verso nord e trova le guardie... o quel che ne resta.',objectives_loc9='La Guardia Thomas ti ha chiesto di risalire il fiume verso nord alla ricerca di Rolf e Malakai, le due guardie scomparse.' WHERE entry=37; /* title: Find the Lost Guards */ /* details: A few days ago we sent two Guards, Rolf and Malakai, to investigate along the river, and they have not yet returned.  To complete my report, I must know what happened to those men.$B$BTravel north along the river and find the guards... or their remains. */ /* objectives: Guard Thomas wants you to travel north up the river and search for the two lost guards, Rolf and Malakai. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Sufato di Westfall',details_loc9='Help me make some Westfall Stew!  Come back with the following ingredients: $b $b 3 Stringy Vulture Meat $b 3 Goretusk Snouts $b 3 Murloc Eyes $b 3 Okra' WHERE entry=38; /* title: Westfall Stew */ /* details: Help me make some Westfall Stew!  Come back with the following ingredients: $B $B 3 Stringy Vulture Meat $B 3 Goretusk Snouts $B 3 Murloc Eyes $B 3 Okra */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Deliver Thomas\' Report',details_loc9='Tell Marshal Dughan of Malakai and Rolf\'s deaths, and report to him that the Murlocs in eastern Elwynn cannot be contained by our current troop presence.$b$bI know we don\'t have many troops to spare, but hopefully Dughan can find someone.' WHERE entry=39; /* title: Deliver Thomas\' Report */ /* details: Tell Marshal Dughan of Malakai and Rolf\'s deaths, and report to him that the Murlocs in eastern Elwynn cannot be contained by our current troop presence.$B$BI know we don\'t have many troops to spare, but hopefully Dughan can find someone. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Pericolo dall\'acqua',details_loc9='$n, c\'è una nuova minaccia nella Foresta di Elwynn! I Murloc stanno risalendo i corsi d\'acqua nella parte orientale di Elwynn, spaventando i pesci e attaccando la popolazione!$b$bHo avvertito il Maresciallo Dughan, ma non ha voluto darmi ascolto. Non crede che i Murloc rappresentino un pericolo, teme di più gli Gnoll e i banditi.$b$bTi prego, $n, va\' a parlare con Dughan e convincilo a mandare altre truppe a est!',objectives_loc9='Remy "Due Volte" ti ha chiesto di parlare con il Maresciallo Dughan a Borgodoro.' WHERE entry=40; /* title: A Fishy Peril */ /* details: $N, there\'s a new threat in Elwynn Forest!  Murlocs are swimming up the streams of eastern Elwynn, scaring away fish and attacking gentle folk!$B$BI warned Marshal Dughan, but he\'s more worried about the gnolls and the bandits.  He\'s not convinced that the murlocs are a danger.$B$BPlease, $N, speak to Dughan and persuade him to send more troops to the east! */ /* objectives: Remy "Two Times" wants you to speak with Marshal Dughan in Goldshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Il destino di Rolf',details_loc9='<Dopo aver esaminato la zona in maniera più approfondita, scopri delle impronte palmate che si dirigono verso est, lungo la costa del Lago del Memoriale. In lontananza riesci a scorgere un villaggio dei Murloc.>$b$b<Forse Rolf ha trovato la morte proprio lì...>',objectives_loc9='Perlustra il villaggio dei Murloc in cerca di Rolf o di prove della sua morte.' WHERE entry=45; /* title: Discover Rolf\'s Fate */ /* details: Upon further searching the area, you find webbed footprints leading east along the shore of Stone Cairn Lake.  In the distance to the east, you can just barely see a Murloc village.$B$BPerhaps Rolf\'s fate ended there... */ /* objectives: Search the murloc village for Rolf, or signs of his death. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Taglia sui Murloc',objectives_loc9='Consegna 8 Pinne di Murloc Strappate alla Guardia Thomas presso il ponte di Elwynn a est.' WHERE entry=46; /* title: Bounty on Murlocs */ /* objectives: Bring 8 Torn Murloc Fins to Guard Thomas at the east Elwynn bridge. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Alla ricerca della Polvere d\'Oro',objectives_loc9='Consegna 10 Mucchi di Polvere d\'Oro a Remy "Due Volte" nella città di Borgodoro. Puoi raccogliere la Polvere d\'Oro dai Coboldi nella Foresta di Elwynn.' WHERE entry=47; /* title: Gold Dust Exchange */ /* objectives: Bring 10 Gold Dust to Remy "Two Times" in Goldshire.  Gold Dust is gathered from Kobolds in Elwynn Forest. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Proteggere la frontiera',details_loc9='Salute, $n. Gli animali selvaggi diventano sempre più aggressivi man mano che ci allontaniamo da Borgodoro, e il Campo di Taglio di Vallevante è vittima di attacchi costanti da parte di lupi e orsi!$b$bAbbiamo bisogno del tuo aiuto.' WHERE entry=52; /* title: Protect the Frontier */ /* details: Hail, $N.  Wild animals are growing more and more aggressive the farther we get from Goldshire, and the Eastvale Logging Camp suffers nearly constant attacks from wolves and bears!$B$BWe could use your help out here. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rapporto a Borgodoro',details_loc9='$n, hai dimostrato valore nel difendere la Contea del Nord. Ora, ti affido l\'incarico di proteggere l\'area circostante alla Foresta di Elwynn.$b$bSe decidi di accettare, sappi che ho preparato dei documenti che devono essere consegnati al Maresciallo Dughan a Borgodoro, lungo la strada che porta a sud, oltre la barriera di confine.' WHERE entry=54; /* title: Report to Goldshire */ /* details: $N, you are a $c with proven interest in the security of Northshire.  You are now tasked with the protection of the surrounding Elwynn Forest.$B$BIf you accept this duty, then I have prepared papers that must be delivered to Marshal Dughan in Goldshire.  Goldshire lies along the southern road, past the border gates. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Armature di stoffa e cuoio',objectives_loc9='Consegna il Buono per un\'Armatura di Roccavento a Sara Timberlain.' WHERE entry=59; /* title: Cloth and Leather Armor */ /* objectives: Give Sara Timberlain the Stormwind Armor Marker. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Candele dei Coboldi',objectives_loc9='Porta 8 Candele Grandi a William Pestel a Borgodoro.' WHERE entry=60; /* title: Kobold Candles */ /* objectives: Bring 8 Large Candles to William Pestle in Goldshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La Miniera Antrocupo',details_loc9='La miniera della Contea del Nord non è l\'unica ad avere problemi! Secondo i rapporti che ho ricevuto, anche la Miniera Antrocupo a Elwynn è stata occupata dai Coboldi.$b$bLa miniera si trova a sud di Borgodoro, tra le fattorie dei Pietradura e dei Maclure. Vai là ed esplorala per confermare questi rapporti, poi torna da me.',objectives_loc9='Esplora la Miniera Antrocupo, poi torna dal Maresciallo Dughan a Borgodoro.' WHERE entry=62; /* title: The Fargodeep Mine */ /* details: The mine in Northshire isn\'t the only one with problems!  I have reports that the Fargodeep Mine in Elwynn has also become a haven for Kobolds.$B$BExplore the mine and confirm these reports, then return to me.  The mine is almost due south of Goldshire, between the Stonefield and Maclure homesteads. */ /* objectives: Explore the Fargodeep Mine, then return to Marshal Dughan in Goldshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Forgotten Heirloom',details_loc9='It was horrible!  Verna woke me when she heard a ruckus in the fields.  The fields were full of hooligans.  We left in a rush and I forgot to pack my pocket watch.  Verna\'s pa gave me that watch on our wedding day and I feel just sick knowing those thieves have it.  I left the pocket watch in the wardrobe at the farmhouse.  Look for the field of pumpkins to the West -- you can\'t miss it.  If you bring it back to me, I\'d sure be grateful!' WHERE entry=64; /* title: The Forgotten Heirloom */ /* details: It was horrible!  Verna woke me when she heard a ruckus in the fields.  The fields were full of hooligans.  We left in a rush and I forgot to pack my pocket watch.  Verna\'s pa gave me that watch on our wedding day and I feel just sick knowing those thieves have it.  I left the pocket watch in the wardrobe at the farmhouse.  Look for the field of pumpkins to the West -- you can\'t miss it.  If you bring it back to me, I\'d sure be grateful! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood',details_loc9='The band of wretches responsible for driving the good people of Westfall from the land call themselves The Defias Brotherhood.  I need you to infiltrate this clan of thugs.  We need to know who heads up the cartel and where they are hiding out.  In Lakeshire, in the inn, there is a rogue by the name of Wiley who owes me a favor.$b$bTravel to Lakeshire in the Redridge Mountains, east of Elwynn, and find out what you can.' WHERE entry=65; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */ /* details: The band of wretches responsible for driving the good people of Westfall from the land call themselves The Defias Brotherhood.  I need you to infiltrate this clan of thugs.  We need to know who heads up the cartel and where they are hiding out.  In Lakeshire, in the inn, there is a rogue by the name of Wiley who owes me a favor.$B$BTravel to Lakeshire in the Redridge Mountains, east of Elwynn, and find out what you can. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='Last night a horrible disturbance rippled through my veins.  I sensed that my granddaughter, Alyssa, was in great danger.  I consulted the cards and Death stared up at me from the table.$b$bAfter taking a long journey through a dark trance I was able to uncover a clue to this terrifying mystery.  A name came to me, the name of Stalvan.$b$bSeek out the Clerk in the Town Hall and see if you can find out more about this character.  I fear for us all.' WHERE entry=66; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: Last night a horrible disturbance rippled through my veins.  I sensed that my granddaughter, Alyssa, was in great danger.  I consulted the cards and Death stared up at me from the table.$B$BAfter taking a long journey through a dark trance I was able to uncover a clue to this terrifying mystery.  A name came to me, the name of Stalvan.$B$BSeek out the Clerk in the Town Hall and see if you can find out more about this character.  I fear for us all. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan' WHERE entry=67; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[You find a Dusty Unsent Letter in the old footlocker.]' WHERE entry=68; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: You find a Dusty Unsent Letter in the old footlocker. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan' WHERE entry=69; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[The name Stalvan rings a bell.  I remember now.$b$bMany years back, on a stormy night, a messenger came in, seeking refuge for the night.  Near the stroke of midnight, the man ran down the stairs screaming, his face pale with fear.  Still wearing his bedclothes, he disappeared into the downpour.$b$bIn his haste he forgot his letters in the chest upstairs.  He never returned for them. One remains from that Stalvan fellow, intended for the Canal District in Stormwind.  Help yourself to it.]' WHERE entry=70; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: The name Stalvan rings a bell.  I remember now.$B$BMany years back, on a stormy night, a messenger came in, seeking refuge for the night.  Near the stroke of midnight, the man ran down the stairs screaming, his face pale with fear.  Still wearing his bedclothes, he disappeared into the downpour.$B$BIn his haste he forgot his letters in the chest upstairs.  He never returned for them. One remains from that Stalvan fellow, intended for the Canal District in Stormwind.  Help yourself to it. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A rapporto da Thomas',details_loc9='Ora che hai entrambi i medaglioni, consegnali alla Guardia Thomas presso il ponte, in modo che sappia che le sue guardie sono state uccise.',objectives_loc9='Consegna i Medaglioni di Rolf e Malakai alla Guardia Thomas presso il ponte di Elwynn a est.' WHERE entry=71; /* title: Report to Thomas */ /* details: Now that you have both medallions, deliver them to Guard Thomas at the bridge so that he might know the fate of his murdered guards. */ /* objectives: Deliver Rolf and Malakai\'s Medallions to Guard Thomas at the eastern Elwynn bridge. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[My father was the caretaker of the estate long before I was.  He had to mop the blood up after the massacre.  But that\'s neither here nor there.$b$bThe last funds of the Flintridge trust have dried up.  Now the last of the family possessions are headed for auction.  Blame the tax vultures.  I guess if you\'re really itching to learn more you\'re free to look through this junk.  Who knows what you might find.]' WHERE entry=72; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: My father was the caretaker of the estate long before I was.  He had to mop the blood up after the massacre.  But that\'s neither here nor there.$B$BThe last funds of the Flintridge trust have dried up.  Now the last of the family possessions are headed for auction.  Blame the tax vultures.  I guess if you\'re really itching to learn more you\'re free to look through this junk.  Who knows what you might find. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[Inside the crate you find various objects: musty heirlooms, a family portrait, a few hunting trophies and some old books.  Near the bottom, underneath a ceramic vase, you uncover A Torn Journal Page.]' WHERE entry=74; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: Inside the crate you find various objects: musty heirlooms, a family portrait, a few hunting trophies and some old books.  Near the bottom, underneath a ceramic vase, you uncover A Torn Journal Page. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[There was a bundle of parchments in the chest upstairs when I moved into this place.  I looked at them once when I first arrived but I gave up once the fog hazed over my peepers. $b$bDo an old, nearly-blind man a favor and check the chest upstairs for anything that might help you in your quest to discover more about this Stalvan character.  I\'m pretty sure there\'s a faded journal page that might be of interest to you.  Bring it to me and I\'ll help in anyway I can.]' WHERE entry=75; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: There was a bundle of parchments in the chest upstairs when I moved into this place.  I looked at them once when I first arrived but I gave up once the fog hazed over my peepers. $B$BDo an old, nearly-blind man a favor and check the chest upstairs for anything that might help you in your quest to discover more about this Stalvan character.  I\'m pretty sure there\'s a faded journal page that might be of interest to you.  Bring it to me and I\'ll help in anyway I can. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La Miniera Venarossa',details_loc9='Grazie a te ora sappiamo che la Miniera Antrocupo è infestata dai Coboldi. Vorrei che esplorassi la Miniera Venarossa per verificare la presenza di quelle creature anche lì.$b$bPer raggiungere la miniera, segui la strada a est fino alla Torre di Azora e da lì dirigiti a nord. La miniera si trova ai piedi delle colline.',objectives_loc9='Esplora la Miniera Venarossa, poi fai rapporto al Maresciallo Dughan nella città di Borgodoro.' WHERE entry=76; /* title: The Jasperlode Mine */ /* details: Thanks to you we know the Fargodeep Mine is infested with kobolds.  Now we need a scout to investigate the more distant Jasperlode Mine.$B$BExplore Jasperlode and confirm any kobold presence.  To reach the mine, travel east along the road until you reach the Tower of Azora.  From the tower, head north and you\'ll find the mine in the foothills. */ /* objectives: Explore the Jasperlode Mine, then report back to Marshal Dughan in Goldshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[I know of someone who might be able to assist you.  Back when I was leading the Stormwind Guard, we used to get drinks at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire.  The Innkeeper there, Smitts, was quite an expert on the local lore.  Show him this page and see what he has to say about it.]' WHERE entry=78; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: I know of someone who might be able to assist you.  Back when I was leading the Stormwind Guard, we used to get drinks at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire.  The Innkeeper there, Smitts, was quite an expert on the local lore.  Show him this page and see what he has to say about it. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[I followed the legend of that Stalvan character for years.  When those visiting nobles were slaughtered a few years back I went with Haggard to investigate.  I found these muddy pages but we were never able to link the handwriting to that crazy man in the woods.  Your trail of evidence proves his guilt.  Take this to Commander Ebonlocke immediately and fill her in on what you\'ve discovered!]' WHERE entry=79; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: I followed the legend of that Stalvan character for years.  When those visiting nobles were slaughtered a few years back I went with Haggard to investigate.  I found these muddy pages but we were never able to link the handwriting to that crazy man in the woods.  Your trail of evidence proves his guilt.  Take this to Commander Ebonlocke immediately and fill her in on what you\'ve discovered! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[I have had my eye on that creep, Stalvan, for quite sometime.  But if this page was written by the same hand it proves his guilt beyond a shadow of a doubt.$b$bIn all his days keeping the Town Registry, Clerk Daltry has become an expert at identifying handwriting.  Show him this page and see if the writing matches that of the registry signature.]' WHERE entry=80; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: I have had my eye on that creep, Stalvan, for quite sometime.  But if this page was written by the same hand it proves his guilt beyond a shadow of a doubt.$B$BIn all his days keeping the Town Registry, Clerk Daltry has become an expert at identifying handwriting.  Show him this page and see if the writing matches that of the registry signature. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Noxious Lair Investigation',details_loc9='All right now, these reports about the bugs... what we know is that they are draining the water pools that used to be where the Noxious Lair is. What we DON\'T know is, well, everything else.$b$bLet\'s figure out who our enemy is first! I want you to head into the Noxious Lair and get some parts off of those critters. Get five from the Centipaar there and bring them to Alchemist Pestlezugg for him to dink with. With him on the case, we\'ll figure out what they are!' WHERE entry=82; /* title: Noxious Lair Investigation */ /* details: All right now, these reports about the bugs... what we know is that they are draining the water pools that used to be where the Noxious Lair is. What we DON\'T know is, well, everything else.$B$BLet\'s figure out who our enemy is first! I want you to head into the Noxious Lair and get some parts off of those critters. Get five from the Centipaar there and bring them to Alchemist Pestlezugg for him to dink with. With him on the case, we\'ll figure out what they are! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Capi di lino eleganti' WHERE entry=83; /* title: Red Linen Goods */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ritorno da Billy',details_loc9='Ecco qua. Quando consegnerai questo pasticcio a Billy, digli che spero gli vada di traverso!',objectives_loc9='Porta il Pasticcio di Carne di Cinghiale a Billy Maclure presso le Vigne dei Maclure.' WHERE entry=84; /* title: Back to Billy */ /* details: Here you go.  And when you give this pie to that Billy, you tell him I hope he chokes on it! */ /* objectives: Bring the Pork Belly Pie to Billy Maclure at the Maclure Vineyards. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La collana rubata',objectives_loc9='Parla con Billy Maclure.' WHERE entry=85; /* title: Lost Necklace */ /* objectives: Speak with Billy Maclure. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Un pasticcio per Billy' WHERE entry=86; /* title: Pie for Billy */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Goldtooth',objectives_loc9='Porta la Collana di Bernice a "Zia" Bernice Pietradura nella Fattoria dei Pietradura.' WHERE entry=87; /* title: Goldtooth */ /* objectives: Bring Bernice\'s Necklace to "Auntie" Bernice Stonefield at the Stonefield Farm. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Principessa deve morire!',objectives_loc9='Uccidi Principessa, prendi il suo collare e riportalo a Ma Pietradura nella Fattoria dei Pietradura.' WHERE entry=88; /* title: Princess Must Die! */ /* objectives: Kill Princess, grab her collar, then bring it back to Ma Stonefield at the Stonefield Farm. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Everstill Bridge',details_loc9='During the last orc invasion we were forced to smelt our iron down to make bullets, swords and armor.  We sent word to Stormwind for a new shipment of materials but a band of Redridge gnolls hijacked the caravan and ran off into the hills behind Lakeshire.$b$bNow we\'re coming up short on supplies to get this bridge rebuilt.  If you can bring me 5 iron pikes and 5 iron rivets, $n, I\'ll make sure you\'re rewarded. $b$bNow let\'s get to work!' WHERE entry=89; /* title: The Everstill Bridge */ /* details: During the last orc invasion we were forced to smelt our iron down to make bullets, swords and armor.  We sent word to Stormwind for a new shipment of materials but a band of Redridge gnolls hijacked the caravan and ran off into the hills behind Lakeshire.$B$BNow we\'re coming up short on supplies to get this bridge rebuilt.  If you can bring me 5 iron pikes and 5 iron rivets, $N, I\'ll make sure you\'re rewarded. $B$BNow let\'s get to work! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Seasoned Wolf Kabobs',details_loc9='Seasoned Wolf Kabobs are a house favorite!  Sure, I can make you some.  But first I\'ll need the supplies.  Bring me 10 Lean Wolf Flanks as well as some Stormwind Seasoning Herbs.  There are so many wolves here in the forest, I am sure finding the Flanks will be no problem.  For the herbs, seek out Felicia Gump in her canal district flower shop in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=90; /* title: Seasoned Wolf Kabobs */ /* details: Seasoned Wolf Kabobs are a house favorite!  Sure, I can make you some.  But first I\'ll need the supplies.  Bring me 10 Lean Wolf Flanks as well as some Stormwind Seasoning Herbs.  There are so many wolves here in the forest, I am sure finding the Flanks will be no problem.  For the herbs, seek out Felicia Gump in her canal district flower shop in Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Solomon\'s Law',details_loc9='An enemy of Stormwind has taken up residence in the eastern foothills of Redridge. This wicked villain uses the Arcane to spread terror and misery upon our town and our people. Under the name, Morganth, he conducts his evil business.$b$bMorganth now controls the Shadowhide Gnoll Clan to perform his biddings. As stated by the Law of Lakeshire, aiding a criminal of the Kingdom is punishable by death.$b$bThese vile gnolls must be killed!$b$bTurn in 10 Shadowhide Pendants to me, and you shall be rewarded.' WHERE entry=91; /* title: Solomon\'s Law */ /* details: An enemy of Stormwind has taken up residence in the eastern foothills of Redridge. This wicked villain uses the Arcane to spread terror and misery upon our town and our people. Under the name, Morganth, he conducts his evil business.$B$BMorganth now controls the Shadowhide Gnoll Clan to perform his biddings. As stated by the Law of Lakeshire, aiding a criminal of the Kingdom is punishable by death.$B$BThese vile gnolls must be killed!$B$BTurn in 10 Shadowhide Pendants to me, and you shall be rewarded. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Gulasch alla Crestarossa',details_loc9='Nothing would please me more than to make you some Redridge Goulash. But there\'s a slight problem. During the recent orc uprising I fed the entire brigade of Stormwind troops. My cupboard is now bare. But if you can provide me with the ingredients, I\'d be happy to oblige.$b$bJust bring me five pieces of Tough Condor Meat, five Great Goretusk Snouts and five helpings of Crisp Spider Meat.' WHERE entry=92; /* title: Redridge Goulash */ /* details: Nothing would please me more than to make you some Redridge Goulash. But there\'s a slight problem. During the recent orc uprising I fed the entire brigade of Stormwind troops. My cupboard is now bare. But if you can provide me with the ingredients, I\'d be happy to oblige.$B$BJust bring me five pieces of Tough Condor Meat, five Great Goretusk Snouts and five helpings of Crisp Spider Meat. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Sven\'s Revenge',details_loc9='I used to work one of the farms to the southeast...until Dark Riders from Deadwind Pass descended upon my farm and slaughtered my family when I was away!$b$bWhen I returned I saw a shadowy figure skulking near my barn, burying something.  He fled before I could catch him, and I couldn\'t linger for I was hot on the heels of the Dark Riders.  So I never discovered what was hidden.$b$bIf you can find what that shadowy figure buried, I would be grateful.  The hiding spot is behind the old stump near my barn.' WHERE entry=95; /* title: Sven\'s Revenge */ /* details: I used to work one of the farms to the southeast...until Dark Riders from Deadwind Pass descended upon my farm and slaughtered my family when I was away!$B$BWhen I returned I saw a shadowy figure skulking near my barn, burying something.  He fled before I could catch him, and I couldn\'t linger for I was hot on the heels of the Dark Riders.  So I never discovered what was hidden.$B$BIf you can find what that shadowy figure buried, I would be grateful.  The hiding spot is behind the old stump near my barn. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan' WHERE entry=97; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Legend of Stalvan',details_loc9='[Stalvan Mistmantle led a life of depravity.  Innocent victims died by his hand.  Undoubtedly he is guilty of countless crimes.  Now the lunatic threatens Darkshire.  The Light only knows what sordid acts he is plotting.  Travel to his cottage just north of town, $c, and execute Stalvan, once and for all.$b$bWhen the deed is done, travel to Madame Eva\'s and show her his family ring.  After all, it was her premonition that led to this gruesome discovery.  But Darkshire is safer because of her.]' WHERE entry=98; /* title: The Legend of Stalvan */ /* details: Stalvan Mistmantle led a life of depravity.  Innocent victims died by his hand.  Undoubtedly he is guilty of countless crimes.  Now the lunatic threatens Darkshire.  The Light only knows what sordid acts he is plotting.  Travel to his cottage just north of town, $C, and execute Stalvan, once and for all.$B$BWhen the deed is done, travel to Madame Eva\'s and show her his family ring.  After all, it was her premonition that led to this gruesome discovery.  But Darkshire is safer because of her. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Arugal\'s Folly',details_loc9='As my understanding of Arugal\'s magic grows so does my disdain for the hapless fool.  I am close to completing my research on his so called remedy.$b$bMy knowledge will be complete when I learn what enchantment is causing the strange behavior going on in Pyrewood Village.  By day, the peasants appear to be Human.  But when the sun goes down the townsfolk turn into Moonrage Worgen.$b$bI need to draw energy from the enchanted shackles Arugal cast on them.  Bring to me six enchanted Pyrewood Shackles, $n.' WHERE entry=99; /* title: Arugal\'s Folly */ /* details: As my understanding of Arugal\'s magic grows so does my disdain for the hapless fool.  I am close to completing my research on his so called remedy.$B$BMy knowledge will be complete when I learn what enchantment is causing the strange behavior going on in Pyrewood Village.  By day, the peasants appear to be Human.  But when the sun goes down the townsfolk turn into Moonrage Worgen.$B$BI need to draw energy from the enchanted shackles Arugal cast on them.  Bring to me six enchanted Pyrewood Shackles, $N. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Totem of Infliction',details_loc9='As the mystical taint creeps through the forest, the need for self-protection is undeniable, $n.  The winds whisper to me and they speak of a great danger which waits patiently for you in the near future.$b$bIf you wish to protect yourself, noble $c, bring to me 10 ghoul fangs, 10 skeleton fingers and 5 vials of spider venom.  For you I shall enchant a Totem of Infliction which will harm those who attempt violent acts against you.' WHERE entry=101; /* title: The Totem of Infliction */ /* details: As the mystical taint creeps through the forest, the need for self-protection is undeniable, $N.  The winds whisper to me and they speak of a great danger which waits patiently for you in the near future.$B$BIf you wish to protect yourself, noble $c, bring to me 10 ghoul fangs, 10 skeleton fingers and 5 vials of spider venom.  For you I shall enchant a Totem of Infliction which will harm those who attempt violent acts against you. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Patrolling Westfall',details_loc9='Stormwind has abandoned us.  A foul wind of depravity rustles through the plains of Westfall.  This was my homeland and I will not turn my back on the citizens who choose to remain here.  We, the former farmers, shall make our stand.$b$bYour task, should you choose to accept, is to patrol the grasslands of Westfall.  Track down and slay the vile Gnolls that seem to be working in conjunction with the Deadmines thieves. Bring me eight Gnoll Paws and I will reward your bravery.' WHERE entry=102; /* title: Patrolling Westfall */ /* details: Stormwind has abandoned us.  A foul wind of depravity rustles through the plains of Westfall.  This was my homeland and I will not turn my back on the citizens who choose to remain here.  We, the former farmers, shall make our stand.$B$BYour task, should you choose to accept, is to patrol the grasslands of Westfall.  Track down and slay the vile Gnolls that seem to be working in conjunction with the Deadmines thieves. Bring me eight Gnoll Paws and I will reward your bravery. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Giovani amanti',details_loc9='Povera me! Sono innamorata di Tommy Joe Pietradura, ma la rivalità che divide le nostre due famiglie mi impedisce di vederlo. Quanto vorrei posare il mio sguardo sul suo incantevole viso...$b$bPrendi questa lettera e consegnala a Tommy Joe da parte mia. Di solito si trova nei pressi del fiume a ovest della Fattoria dei Pietradura, a ovest di qui.',objectives_loc9='Consegna la Lettera d\'Amore di Maybell a Tommy Joe Pietradura.' WHERE entry=106; /* title: Young Lovers */ /* details: Oh, I\'m cursed!  My heart belongs to Tommy Joe Stonefield, but our families are bitter enemies.  So I can\'t see him, even though my eyes ache to gaze upon that handsome face!$B$BPlease, take this letter and give it to Tommy Joe.  He\'s usually at the river to the west of the Stonefield Farm, which is due west of here. */ /* objectives: Give Maybell\'s Love Letter to Tommy Joe Stonefield. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Nota per William',details_loc9='Scommetto che William Pestel ha una pozione per riunire i nostri due giovani innamorati!$b$bTieni, consegna questa nota a William. Si trova nella Locanda del Fiero Leone a Borgodoro.',objectives_loc9='Consegna la Nota di Nonna Pietradura a William Pestel.' WHERE entry=107; /* title: Note to William */ /* details: I bet William Pestle has a potion to unite our two young lovers!$B$BHere, take this note to William.  He\'s staying at the Lion\'s Pride Inn in Goldshire. */ /* objectives: Take Gramma Stonefield\'s Note to William Pestle. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Report to Gryan Stoutmantle',details_loc9='Looks to me you\'ve seen quite a bit of combat in your time, $c.  If you haven\'t already, you should report to Gryan Stoutmantle.  He heads up the People\'s Militia, aimed at protecting the farmlands of Westfall.  I bet he could use your help.  You can usually find him in the stone tower on Sentinel Hill, just off the road in the middle of Westfall.' WHERE entry=109; /* title: Report to Gryan Stoutmantle */ /* details: Looks to me you\'ve seen quite a bit of combat in your time, $c.  If you haven\'t already, you should report to Gryan Stoutmantle.  He heads up the People\'s Militia, aimed at protecting the farmlands of Westfall.  I bet he could use your help.  You can usually find him in the stone tower on Sentinel Hill, just off the road in the middle of Westfall. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Insect Part Analysis',details_loc9='I\'m going to spend some time taking a look at Scrimshank\'s surveying gear... as well as putting his personal effects in order.  I get the sneaking feeling behind my ears that this isn\'t the last loss we\'ll be facing against these bugs.$b$bI\'d like for you to check in with Alchemist Pestlezugg to see if he has had a chance to process the insect parts we sent him.  If they\'re ready, bring them to me.' WHERE entry=110; /* title: Insect Part Analysis */ /* details: I\'m going to spend some time taking a look at Scrimshank\'s surveying gear... as well as putting his personal effects in order.  I get the sneaking feeling behind my ears that this isn\'t the last loss we\'ll be facing against these bugs.$B$BI\'d like for you to check in with Alchemist Pestlezugg to see if he has had a chance to process the insect parts we sent him.  If they\'re ready, bring them to me. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A colloquio con la nonna',details_loc9='Ti prego, $n, parla con mia nonna. Lei è l\'unica che può aiutarmi a stare insieme a Maybell.$b$bSi trova nella nostra casa a est.',objectives_loc9='Parla con Nonna Pietradura.' WHERE entry=111; /* title: Speak with Gramma */ /* details: Please, $N, talk with my Gramma.  If anyone can find a way to bring me together with Maybell, she can.$B$BShe\'s inside our house east of here. */ /* objectives: Speak with Gramma Stonefield. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Raccolta alghe',objectives_loc9='Porta 4 Fronde d\'Alga di Cristallo a William Pestel nella città di Borgodoro.' WHERE entry=112; /* title: Collecting Kelp */ /* objectives: Bring 4 Crystal Kelp Fronds to William Pestle in Goldshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Insect Part Analysis',details_loc9='Senior Surveyor Fizzledowser needs to see this report immediately.  Actually... everyone who can read needs to see this report.  We are facing a grave and serious threat to not only Tanaris and Gadgetzan, but if left unchecked, the entirety of southern Kalimdor.  Heck, even quite possible the whole of Azeroth; this thing has given no indication it will subside.$b$bHave Fizzledowser make a duplicate of the report for you to distribute freely to your allegiance. Everyone must know about this threat!' WHERE entry=113; /* title: Insect Part Analysis */ /* details: Senior Surveyor Fizzledowser needs to see this report immediately.  Actually... everyone who can read needs to see this report.  We are facing a grave and serious threat to not only Tanaris and Gadgetzan, but if left unchecked, the entirety of southern Kalimdor.  Heck, even quite possible the whole of Azeroth; this thing has given no indication it will subside.$B$BHave Fizzledowser make a duplicate of the report for you to distribute freely to your allegiance. Everyone must know about this threat! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La fuga',details_loc9='Porta questo Liquore dell\'Invisibilità alla giovane Maybell. Dovrebbe durare abbastanza da permetterle di incontrare Tommy Joe.',objectives_loc9='Consegna il Liquore dell\'Invisibilità a Maybell Maclure.' WHERE entry=114; /* title: The Escape */ /* details: Take this invisibility liquor to young Maybell.  It should last long enough for her to visit Tommy Joe. */ /* objectives: Take the Invisibility Liquor to Maybell Maclure. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Price of Shoes',details_loc9='I\'ve been using so much iron keeping the Stormwind Guards outfitted, I don\'t have enough to supply the stable\'s horses with shoes!$b$bTake this note to Blacksmith Argus in Goldshire.  It explains to him my problem and requests a shipment of horseshoes.' WHERE entry=118; /* title: The Price of Shoes */ /* details: I\'ve been using so much iron keeping the Stormwind Guards outfitted, I don\'t have enough to supply the stable\'s horses with shoes!$B$BTake this note to Blacksmith Argus in Goldshire.  It explains to him my problem and requests a shipment of horseshoes. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Underbelly Scales',details_loc9='I need some underbelly scales from black dragon whelps to pay for the shoes Argus sent me from Goldshire.  If you can get 6 of them for me, then I can pay Argus with some... and have enough left to fashion something for you.$b$bBlack dragon whelps are often flying around south of Lakeshire, but they like to wander.  You might have to just keep an eye out and hunt them when you see them.' WHERE entry=122; /* title: Underbelly Scales */ /* details: I need some underbelly scales from black dragon whelps to pay for the shoes Argus sent me from Goldshire.  If you can get 6 of them for me, then I can pay Argus with some... and have enough left to fashion something for you.$B$BBlack dragon whelps are often flying around south of Lakeshire, but they like to wander.  You might have to just keep an eye out and hunt them when you see them. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Il Collezionista' WHERE entry=123; /* title: The Collector */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Baying of Gnolls',details_loc9='As if the attacking orcs weren\'t enough!  Now I have gnoll brutes and mystics prowling along the ridge north of my stable, taking my horses when they stray...$b$bIf you can get rid of those gnolls, my horses and I would be very grateful.' WHERE entry=124; /* title: A Baying of Gnolls */ /* details: As if the attacking orcs weren\'t enough!  Now I have gnoll brutes and mystics prowling along the ridge north of my stable, taking my horses when they stray...$B$BIf you can get rid of those gnolls, my horses and I would be very grateful. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Lost Tools',details_loc9='I could really use a hand here, $n.  With the town under siege, it\'s been hard to get supplies.  My tools were being delivered from Goldshire by wagon but the bridge was blown out.  We put the tools in a boat but the orcs hit it with a catapult.  Just my luck, my toolbox sank right to the bottom of the lake.$b$bRetrieve my toolbox, $n, and I\'ll make it worth your while.' WHERE entry=125; /* title: The Lost Tools */ /* details: I could really use a hand here, $N.  With the town under siege, it\'s been hard to get supplies.  My tools were being delivered from Goldshire by wagon but the bridge was blown out.  We put the tools in a boat but the orcs hit it with a catapult.  Just my luck, my toolbox sank right to the bottom of the lake.$B$BRetrieve my toolbox, $N, and I\'ll make it worth your while. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Selling Fish',details_loc9='Lake Everstill is famous for its spotted sunfish.  There\'s always demand for them...and I\'m running low!$b$bBring me a batch of 10 and I\'ll barter well for them.  If you can\'t fish yourself, then...maybe you can get them off the murlocs!' WHERE entry=127; /* title: Selling Fish */ /* details: Lake Everstill is famous for its spotted sunfish.  There\'s always demand for them...and I\'m running low!$B$BBring me a batch of 10 and I\'ll barter well for them.  If you can\'t fish yourself, then...maybe you can get them off the murlocs! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Free Lunch',details_loc9='Can you do me a favor?  I\'ve prepared a lunch for Guard Parker, but he\'s out on patrol...he\'s a big, strong Stormwind guard who can defend himself, but it\'s much too dangerous out there for a townsperson like me.$b$bSo if you deliver his lunch for me, then come back here and I\'ll give you a free lunch!  Parker patrols the stretch of road leading to Duskwood.' WHERE entry=129; /* title: A Free Lunch */ /* details: Can you do me a favor?  I\'ve prepared a lunch for Guard Parker, but he\'s out on patrol...he\'s a big, strong Stormwind guard who can defend himself, but it\'s much too dangerous out there for a townsperson like me.$B$BSo if you deliver his lunch for me, then come back here and I\'ll give you a free lunch!  Parker patrols the stretch of road leading to Duskwood. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Visit the Herbalist',details_loc9='Before you go back to Darcy, can you bring her some flowers for me?  You can get them at the herbalist shop back in Lakeshire, at the west end of town.$b$bBut when you get the flowers...don\'t tell the herbalist, Martie, whom they\'re from, or whom they\'re for...' WHERE entry=130; /* title: Visit the Herbalist */ /* details: Before you go back to Darcy, can you bring her some flowers for me?  You can get them at the herbalist shop back in Lakeshire, at the west end of town.$B$BBut when you get the flowers...don\'t tell the herbalist, Martie, whom they\'re from, or whom they\'re for... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood',details_loc9='What I am about to tell you could cost me my life.  The Defias gang is up to something big.  Last I heard they were working in conjunction with various gnolls, kobolds and even goblins.$b$bTake this note to Stoutmantle.  It explains as much as I know on the subject.' WHERE entry=132; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */ /* details: What I am about to tell you could cost me my life.  The Defias gang is up to something big.  Last I heard they were working in conjunction with various gnolls, kobolds and even goblins.$B$BTake this note to Stoutmantle.  It explains as much as I know on the subject. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ghoulish Effigy',details_loc9='I live so far from the protection of town, it\'s a wonder the ghouls and the walking dead haven\'t eaten me!  In fact, just yesterday a pack of Bone Chewers was pounding on the walls of my house!$b$bI want to make an effigy - a kind of "scarecrow" for Ghouls.  To do that I need some Ghoul Ribs.  You can get them from Flesh Eaters, Bone Chewers, Brain Eaters, Rotted Ones and Plague Spreaders.$b$bGet the ribs for me, and I will repay you with some coin.' WHERE entry=133; /* title: Ghoulish Effigy */ /* details: I live so far from the protection of town, it\'s a wonder the ghouls and the walking dead haven\'t eaten me!  In fact, just yesterday a pack of Bone Chewers was pounding on the walls of my house!$B$BI want to make an effigy - a kind of "scarecrow" for Ghouls.  To do that I need some Ghoul Ribs.  You can get them from Flesh Eaters, Bone Chewers, Brain Eaters, Rotted Ones and Plague Spreaders.$B$BGet the ribs for me, and I will repay you with some coin. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood' WHERE entry=135; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood',details_loc9='The Stonemasons\' Guild was run by a man named Edwin VanCleef.  VanCleef was responsible for rebuilding Stormwind after the orcs razed it in the First War.  Apparently, VanCleef and his men were unhappy with their treatment by the King after the reconstruction was complete.  That just might explain a thing or two.$b$bI have written a more detailed account for your Master in Westfall.  Take this to him at once!' WHERE entry=141; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */ /* details: The Stonemasons\' Guild was run by a man named Edwin VanCleef.  VanCleef was responsible for rebuilding Stormwind after the orcs razed it in the First War.  Apparently, VanCleef and his men were unhappy with their treatment by the King after the reconstruction was complete.  That just might explain a thing or two.$B$BI have written a more detailed account for your Master in Westfall.  Take this to him at once! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood' WHERE entry=142; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Manhunt',details_loc9='Questo "Collezionista" sta rubando l\'oro dalle nostre miniere! Voglio che lo consegni alla giustizia e mi porti l\'anello citato nel programma di raccolta che mi hai consegnato. Potrebbe dirci per chi lavora...$b$bSecondo il programma, il Collezionista si nasconderebbe nel Campo di Zucche dei Pozzonero. Vai lì e trovalo.' WHERE entry=147; /* title: Manhunt */ /* details: If the "Collector" is taking gold from our mines then he\'s stealing from the kingdom!  Bring the Collector to justice, and bring me the ring mentioned in the pickup schedule you gave me.  It may tell us whom the Collector is working for...$B$BThat Pickup Schedule says the Collector is hiding out at the Brackwell Pumpkin Patch.  You should search for him there. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Supplies from Darkshire',details_loc9='Oh, what is a poor old man to do?  I need some supplies from Darkshire, but the village is so far away and I am so old and feeble...I would never make the trip.$b$bCan you go to Darkshire and bring me back some Ghost Hair Thread?  You can get it from Madame Eva at her home on the Darkshire square.' WHERE entry=148; /* title: Supplies from Darkshire */ /* details: Oh, what is a poor old man to do?  I need some supplies from Darkshire, but the village is so far away and I am so old and feeble...I would never make the trip.$B$BCan you go to Darkshire and bring me back some Ghost Hair Thread?  You can get it from Madame Eva at her home on the Darkshire square. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Murloc Poachers',details_loc9='Murlocs are becoming a problem.  Larger groups of the fishmen are dropping anchor along the shores of Lake Everstill and fishing up a storm!  We need them gone before they eat all the fish in the lake!$b$bHunt murlocs!  Bring me eight of their fins and I might have something for you...' WHERE entry=150; /* title: Murloc Poachers */ /* details: Murlocs are becoming a problem.  Larger groups of the fishmen are dropping anchor along the shores of Lake Everstill and fishing up a storm!  We need them gone before they eat all the fish in the lake!$B$BHunt murlocs!  Bring me eight of their fins and I might have something for you... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Poor Old Blanchy',details_loc9='Poor Old Blanchy!  Such a tired beast after all the work we put her through. I fed her before we left the farm, but we weren\'t expecting the wagon to break on us. If you could bring her a few handfuls of oats from the fields, I\'d be grateful.$b$bI bet you could find some around all of the farms in Westfall, if you can steer clear of those horrific machines that have taken over. There are several farms southwest of here.' WHERE entry=151; /* title: Poor Old Blanchy */ /* details: Poor Old Blanchy!  Such a tired beast after all the work we put her through. I fed her before we left the farm, but we weren\'t expecting the wagon to break on us. If you could bring her a few handfuls of oats from the fields, I\'d be grateful.$B$BI bet you could find some around all of the farms in Westfall, if you can steer clear of those horrific machines that have taken over. There are several farms southwest of here. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Coast Isn\'t Clear',details_loc9='You probably noticed all of the shipwrecks along the coast.  The Great Sea is treacherous indeed.  The coast of Westfall needs to be kept clear, so that if sailors find their way to our beaches, they are safe.  The Murlocs are trouble though.$b$bKill 7 Tidehunters, 7 Warriors, 7 Oracles and 7 Coastrunners and I will see to it that you are rewarded.' WHERE entry=152; /* title: The Coast Isn\'t Clear */ /* details: You probably noticed all of the shipwrecks along the coast.  The Great Sea is treacherous indeed.  The coast of Westfall needs to be kept clear, so that if sailors find their way to our beaches, they are safe.  The Murlocs are trouble though.$B$BKill 7 Tidehunters, 7 Warriors, 7 Oracles and 7 Coastrunners and I will see to it that you are rewarded. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Red Leather Bandanas',details_loc9='The Defias Front is constantly shifting.  I\'ve been following their movements for quite some time now.  On a side note, I\'ve ascertained that many members of the gang can be tracked by the Red Leather Bandanas they wear.$b$bBring me 15 of these Bandanas and I\'ll see to it you are rewarded.' WHERE entry=153; /* title: Red Leather Bandanas */ /* details: The Defias Front is constantly shifting.  I\'ve been following their movements for quite some time now.  On a side note, I\'ve ascertained that many members of the gang can be tracked by the Red Leather Bandanas they wear.$B$BBring me 15 of these Bandanas and I\'ll see to it you are rewarded. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Return the Comb',details_loc9='NO!!!!!$b$bTake it, take this comb away from me!$b$bI\'m a monster, and no one will ever think me lovely again!',objectives_loc9='Riconsegna il Pettine con Capelli Spettrali a Dama Eva nel villaggio di Borgoscuro.' WHERE entry=154; /* title: Return the Comb */ /* details: NO!!!!!$B$BTake it, take this comb away from me!$B$BI\'m a monster, and no one will ever think me lovely again! */ /* objectives: Return the Ghost Hair Comb to Madame Eva in Darkshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood' WHERE entry=155; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Zombie Juice',details_loc9='I need a bottle of a certain liquor - Zombie Juice.  Tavernkeep Smitts at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire should have some.$b$bAnd please hurry, $n.  These nights get cold, and I need that drink to put fire in my veins again!',objectives_loc9='Parla con il Taverniere Smitts.' WHERE entry=158; /* title: Zombie Juice */ /* details: I need a bottle of a certain liquor - Zombie Juice.  Tavernkeep Smitts at the Scarlet Raven Tavern in Darkshire should have some.$B$BAnd please hurry, $N.  These nights get cold, and I need that drink to put fire in my veins again! */ /* objectives: Speak with Tavernkeep Smitts. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rise of the Silithid' WHERE entry=162; /* title: Rise of the Silithid */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Raven Hill',details_loc9='Something\'s amiss at Raven Hill, $n. Calor swears that someone--or something--is haunting the buildings there. Two nights running he\'s noticed the shadows moving, and the third before that he says he saw light in one of the windows.$b$bIf, as you say, you care about the safety of Duskwood, find out what monster haunts in Raven Hill.' WHERE entry=163; /* title: Raven Hill */ /* details: Something\'s amiss at Raven Hill, $n. Calor swears that someone--or something--is haunting the buildings there. Two nights running he\'s noticed the shadows moving, and the third before that he says he saw light in one of the windows.$B$BIf, as you say, you care about the safety of Duskwood, find out what monster haunts in Raven Hill. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Deliveries to Sven',details_loc9='Do you know Sven? Now, there is a man who does the work of the Light! He and his followers keep a camp at the northwestern edge of Duskwood.$b$bUnfortunately, because they are so few, they cannot even spare a man to fetch supplies from town. Will you deliver these supplies to him?' WHERE entry=164; /* title: Deliveries to Sven */ /* details: Do you know Sven? Now, there is a man who does the work of the Light! He and his followers keep a camp at the northwestern edge of Duskwood.$B$BUnfortunately, because they are so few, they cannot even spare a man to fetch supplies from town. Will you deliver these supplies to him? */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='L\'eremita',details_loc9='There was an old man who used to come into town to buy supplies rather frequently, but I haven\'t seen him for quite some time now. He lives out in a shack overlooking Raven Hill cemetery, if I remember correctly. Perhaps you should go see if something is amiss.' WHERE entry=165; /* title: The Hermit */ /* details: There was an old man who used to come into town to buy supplies rather frequently, but I haven\'t seen him for quite some time now. He lives out in a shack overlooking Raven Hill cemetery, if I remember correctly. Perhaps you should go see if something is amiss. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Defias Brotherhood',details_loc9='There is but one task left for you to complete.  Edwin VanCleef must be assassinated.  While it saddens me to condemn any man to a death sentence, it is for the greater good of the people of Westfall that VanCleef is laid to rest once and for all.  Bring me the villain\'s head once the deed is done.' WHERE entry=166; /* title: The Defias Brotherhood */ /* details: There is but one task left for you to complete.  Edwin VanCleef must be assassinated.  While it saddens me to condemn any man to a death sentence, it is for the greater good of the people of Westfall that VanCleef is laid to rest once and for all.  Bring me the villain\'s head once the deed is done. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Oh Brother. . .',details_loc9='We were deep in a vast mine in Westfall, hidden beneath a barn in Moonbrook. No clue where these stinkin\' thieving types came from. Anyway, the mine tunnel collapsed on us. I got out but the others... well... the others haven\'t been heard from.$b$bYou look like you might have better luck in there. If you could look for my brother, I\'d be thankful.  He always carried his Explorers\' League Badge. If you can\'t find him, that badge would at least give me some peace of mind.' WHERE entry=167; /* title: Oh Brother. . . */ /* details: We were deep in a vast mine in Westfall, hidden beneath a barn in Moonbrook. No clue where these stinkin\' thieving types came from. Anyway, the mine tunnel collapsed on us. I got out but the others... well... the others haven\'t been heard from.$B$BYou look like you might have better luck in there. If you could look for my brother, I\'d be thankful.  He always carried his Explorers\' League Badge. If you can\'t find him, that badge would at least give me some peace of mind. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ricercato: Gath\'Ilzogg',details_loc9='Wanted! Gath\'Ilzogg, Leader of the Blackrock attacks on Stonewatch Keep and raids against the township of Lakeshire. $b$bGath\'Ilzogg is extremely dangerous.  He is reportedly holed up in the recently conquered keep plotting the Blackrock clan\'s further crimes against humanity.  The orc infestation must be quelled at all costs.  A gracious reward will be given to whatever brave soul can deliver the head of Gath\'Ilzogg to Magistrate Solomon.' WHERE entry=169; /* title: Wanted: Gath\'Ilzogg */ /* details: Wanted! Gath\'Ilzogg, Leader of the Blackrock attacks on Stonewatch Keep and raids against the township of Lakeshire. $B$BGath\'Ilzogg is extremely dangerous.  He is reportedly holed up in the recently conquered keep plotting the Blackrock clan\'s further crimes against humanity.  The orc infestation must be quelled at all costs.  A gracious reward will be given to whatever brave soul can deliver the head of Gath\'Ilzogg to Magistrate Solomon. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Un Guardiano dell\'Alleanza' WHERE entry=171; /* title: A Warden of the Alliance */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Settimana dei Bambini',details_loc9='Vuoi aiutare l\'orfanotrofio? Che tu sia <benedetto/benedetta>! Il tuo aiuto durante la Settimana dei Bambini sarà prezioso.$b$bPrendi questo fischietto. Potrai sfruttarlo per poco tempo, in genere per la durata della Settimana dei Bambini. Usandolo una volta, potrai parlare con il bambino che hai scelto di accompagnare, mentre usandolo una seconda volta, manderai via il bambino.$b$bForza, $n, suona il fischietto! Sono certa che il bambino è ansioso di conoscerti.' WHERE entry=172; /* title: Children\'s Week */ /* details: You\'re willing to help us here at the orphanage?  Bless you, friend; your aid during Children\'s Week will be invaluable.$B$BTake this whistle.  You will only be able to use it for a short amount of time - typically not longer than Children\'s Week itself.  When you use it, you will be able to talk with the child you\'ve agreed to look after.  Using it again will dismiss the child.$B$BBy all means $N - use the whistle and meet your ward!  I\'m sure the child will be most eager to meet you. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Worgen in the Woods',details_loc9='Darkness seems drawn inexorably to Duskwood. Master Carevin\'s quest is the expulsion of evil and heresy. Through our efforts are the people of Darkshire kept safe.$b$bYou believe yourself worthy to join us?$b$bI once thought as you. Disillusioned by the complacency of the Watch, I joined Master Carevin. If you wish to prove yourself, it will not be through words.$b$bTest your skills against the Nightbane Shadow Weaver worgen in Brightwood Grove--bright, hah!--and the Rotting Orchard.' WHERE entry=173; /* title: Worgen in the Woods */ /* details: Darkness seems drawn inexorably to Duskwood. Master Carevin\'s quest is the expulsion of evil and heresy. Through our efforts are the people of Darkshire kept safe.$B$BYou believe yourself worthy to join us?$B$BI once thought as you. Disillusioned by the complacency of the Watch, I joined Master Carevin. If you wish to prove yourself, it will not be through words.$B$BTest your skills against the Nightbane Shadow Weaver worgen in Brightwood Grove--bright, hah!--and the Rotting Orchard. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ricercato: &quot;Boccalarga&quot;' WHERE entry=176; /* title: Wanted:  "Hogger" */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Dwarven Outfitters',details_loc9='What do we have here? You look as though you might need something to keep your hands warm, hm?$b$bI\'ll tell you what would help: a pair of nice, warm gloves. And, being the kind soul that I am, I\'d be more than happy to provide you with a suitable pair. I\'ve one condition, however.$b$bI need you to go get me some wolf meat. Nice arrangement, hm? You bring me some wolf meat, and I\'ll make sure you don\'t lose any digits to frostbite. Well, what do you say?' WHERE entry=179; /* title: Dwarven Outfitters */ /* details: What do we have here? You look as though you might need something to keep your hands warm, hm?$B$BI\'ll tell you what would help: a pair of nice, warm gloves. And, being the kind soul that I am, I\'d be more than happy to provide you with a suitable pair. I\'ve one condition, however.$B$BI need you to go get me some wolf meat. Nice arrangement, hm? You bring me some wolf meat, and I\'ll make sure you don\'t lose any digits to frostbite. Well, what do you say? */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ricercato: Tenente Fangore',details_loc9='Wanted: Lieutenant Fangore$b$bKnown leader of the Shadowhide Gnoll Clan, working under the enemy of the Township and Kingdom, Morganth.  By mandate of Magistrate Solomon, this vile betrayer of Stormwind is wanted dead.  Show his paw to the Magistrate as proof of his death.' WHERE entry=180; /* title: Wanted: Lieutenant Fangore */ /* details: Wanted: Lieutenant Fangore$B$BKnown leader of the Shadowhide Gnoll Clan, working under the enemy of the Township and Kingdom, Morganth.  By mandate of Magistrate Solomon, this vile betrayer of Stormwind is wanted dead.  Show his paw to the Magistrate as proof of his death. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La minaccia dei Troll' WHERE entry=182; /* title: The Troll Cave */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Boar Hunter',details_loc9='Nothing like a day of boar hunting, eh?$b$bThough, here in Coldridge Valley, there are so many boars it almost takes the fun out of it. No need to get them charging. They\'re all angry and ready without any help. In fact, recently, there\'ve been so many boars in the area, it\'s become dangerous for me to do my daily hunting.$b$bLong story short, if you could help me kill some of the boars, I would appreciate it.' WHERE entry=183; /* title: The Boar Hunter */ /* details: Nothing like a day of boar hunting, eh?$B$BThough, here in Coldridge Valley, there are so many boars it almost takes the fun out of it. No need to get them charging. They\'re all angry and ready without any help. In fact, recently, there\'ve been so many boars in the area, it\'s become dangerous for me to do my daily hunting.$B$BLong story short, if you could help me kill some of the boars, I would appreciate it. */
