UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Bloodscalp Ears',details_loc9='Damn trolls! They\'ve been killing off our agents in the jungle! I\'ve already lost a good number of my best guards to skirmishes with them. The costs are piling up! How will I explain this to Baron Revilgaz?$b$bDecisive action... Think, Kebok... you weren\'t assigned to the post you have today for sitting around... I\'ve got it! You... $n, is it? You\'ll help me, won\'t you? There\'s money to be had!$b$bHere\'s the deal... you bring me the ears of fifteen Bloodscalp Trolls, and I\'ll compensate you well.' WHERE entry=189; /* title: Bloodscalp Ears */ /* details: Damn trolls! They\'ve been killing off our agents in the jungle! I\'ve already lost a good number of my best guards to skirmishes with them. The costs are piling up! How will I explain this to Baron Revilgaz?$B$BDecisive action... Think, Kebok... you weren\'t assigned to the post you have today for sitting around... I\'ve got it! You... $n, is it? You\'ll help me, won\'t you? There\'s money to be had!$B$BHere\'s the deal... you bring me the ears of fifteen Bloodscalp Trolls, and I\'ll compensate you well. */
