UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Decisive Strike' WHERE entry=217; /* title: In Defense of the King\'s Lands */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ghiaccio e fuoco' WHERE entry=218; /* title: The Stolen Journal */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Missing In Action',details_loc9='At last, friends of the Alliance!$b$bHelp... please... $b$bThe last thing I remember these foul Orcs overpowered our regiment.  Most the men were killed. I took a strong blow to the head and everything went black. Now I am held captive in this cave.  Help me, I am hurt badly.$b$bI\'ll need help getting back to town... please... you\'re my last hope...' WHERE entry=219; /* title: Missing In Action */ /* details: At last, friends of the Alliance!$B$BHelp... please... $B$BThe last thing I remember these foul Orcs overpowered our regiment.  Most the men were killed. I took a strong blow to the head and everything went black. Now I am held captive in this cave.  Help me, I am hurt badly.$B$BI\'ll need help getting back to town... please... you\'re my last hope... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Worgen in the Woods',details_loc9='You might have noticed some larger worgen wandering around with the Shadow Weavers in the woods? From what we can tell, these Dark Runners make up the bulk of the worgen numbers.$b$bOn my rangings, I\'ve also noticed that they have overrun the Rotting Orchard southwest of town. These worgen are a bit tougher than the last you faced.$b$bBe on your guard.' WHERE entry=221; /* title: Worgen in the Woods */ /* details: You might have noticed some larger worgen wandering around with the Shadow Weavers in the woods? From what we can tell, these Dark Runners make up the bulk of the worgen numbers.$B$BOn my rangings, I\'ve also noticed that they have overrun the Rotting Orchard southwest of town. These worgen are a bit tougher than the last you faced.$B$BBe on your guard. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Worgen in the Woods',details_loc9='Your previous accomplishments have convinced me that you are ready to take on the toughest worgen infesting the woods.$b$bOf the worgen that have made their new home here, the Vile Fangs and the Tainted Ones have proven the most dangerous. They\'ve settled down near some of the caves and in the mine to the south.$b$bFrom far away you can even see the light from their bonfires...' WHERE entry=222; /* title: Worgen in the Woods */ /* details: Your previous accomplishments have convinced me that you are ready to take on the toughest worgen infesting the woods.$B$BOf the worgen that have made their new home here, the Vile Fangs and the Tainted Ones have proven the most dangerous. They\'ve settled down near some of the caves and in the mine to the south.$B$BFrom far away you can even see the light from their bonfires... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Worgen in the Woods',details_loc9='Here you go, $n. Bring this message to Master Carevin.$b$b<He quickly removes a piece of faded parchment and offers it to you.>$b$bA few more like you, and we will outnumber the Night Watch! Perhaps then we could complete the work that we few carry on today.',objectives_loc9='Consegna la Nota di Calor a Jonathan Carevin.' WHERE entry=223; /* title: Worgen in the Woods */ /* details: Here you go, $n. Bring this message to Master Carevin.$B$B<He quickly removes a piece of faded parchment and offers it to you.>$B$BA few more like you, and we will outnumber the Night Watch! Perhaps then we could complete the work that we few carry on today. */ /* objectives: Bring Calor\'s note to Jonathan Carevin. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Decisive Strike' WHERE entry=224; /* title: In Defense of the King\'s Lands */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Weathered Grave',details_loc9='The weathered grave marker reads simply:$b$bMORGAN LADIMORE$b$b<Upon further examination, you notice that dirt over the grave has been recently disturbed, and that a good amount of the dirt seems to have been displaced...>',objectives_loc9='Parla con Sirra Von\'indi a Borgoscuro.' WHERE entry=225; /* title: The Weathered Grave */ /* details: The weathered grave marker reads simply:$B$BMORGAN LADIMORE$B$B<Upon further examination, you notice that dirt over the grave has been recently disturbed, and that a good amount of the dirt seems to have been displaced...> */ /* objectives: Speak with Sirra Von\'Indi in Darkshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Morgan Ladimore',details_loc9='<Sirra cerca tra gli scaffali e prende un volume rilegato in pelle.>$b$bSe vuoi saperne di più, potresti chiedere ad Althea. È lei che ultimamente si occupa di gestire i... problemi con Morgan.',objectives_loc9='Parla con il Comandante Althea Serranero a Borgoscuro.' WHERE entry=227; /* title: Morgan Ladimore */ /* details: <He searches through the shelves and comes up with a leatherbound book.>$B$BIf you would like to know more, you might ask Althea, she\'s been the one to handle the... trouble... with him of late. */ /* objectives: Speak with Commander Althea Ebonlocke in Darkshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Mor\'Ladim',details_loc9='From what my scouts tell me, Mor\'Ladim wanders throughout Duskwood, following a strange and meandering path through the cemetery. We buried him out past the house on the hill, you know where that is?$b$bThere isn\'t anything I can do to help you, but I wish you good luck.',objectives_loc9='Uccidi Mor\'ladim e consegna il suo teschio al Comandante Althea Serranero nel villaggio di Borgoscuro.' WHERE entry=228; /* title: Mor\'Ladim */ /* details: From what my scouts tell me, Mor\'Ladim wanders throughout Duskwood, following a strange and meandering path through the cemetery. We buried him out past the house on the hill, you know where that is?$B$BThere isn\'t anything I can do to help you, but I wish you good luck. */ /* objectives: Kill Mor\'Ladim, then return his skull to Commander Althea Ebonlocke in Darkshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Daughter Who Lived',details_loc9='I should have told you this earlier...$b$bHow do I put this...$b$bMorgan may have believed that his family was all dead, but, in fact, his daughter Sarah Ladimore is now a Watcher. She\'s always been troubled by the... circumstances... surrounding her father\'s death. Perhaps you could go to bring the news to her.',objectives_loc9='Parla con la Guardiana Sarah Ladimore a Borgoscuro.' WHERE entry=229; /* title: The Daughter Who Lived */ /* details: I should have told you this earlier...$B$BHow do I put this...$B$BMorgan may have believed that his family was all dead, but, in fact, his daughter Sarah Ladimore is now a Watcher. She\'s always been troubled by the... circumstances... surrounding her father\'s death. Perhaps you could go to bring the news to her. */ /* objectives: Speak with Watcher Sarah Ladimore in Darkshire. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Daughter\'s Love',details_loc9='Here, take this and lay it on his grave. Maybe... somehow, he\'ll know that I\'m okay, and that none of us hold him responsible for what happened.$b$b<There are tears in her eyes now, as she slides a ring from her right hand, and presses it into your hands.>$b$bAnd... thank you, $n.',objectives_loc9='Porta l\'Anello di Sarah Ladimore sulla tomba di Morgan Ladimore.' WHERE entry=231; /* title: A Daughter\'s Love */ /* details: Here, take this and lay it on his grave. Maybe... somehow, he\'ll know that I\'m okay, and that none of us hold him responsible for what happened.$B$B<There are tears in her eyes now, as she slides a ring from her right hand, and presses it into your hands.>$B$BAnd... thank you, $n. */ /* objectives: Take Sarah Ladimore\'s ring to Morgan Ladimore\'s grave. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Errand for Apothecary Zinge',details_loc9='The Royal Apothecary Society needs your assistance.  Listen closely, and both of us may profit from my plan.$b$bApothecary Keever in the next room may be... touched... but his research does potentially bear fruit if it were pursued by a clever researcher.  Fortunately, I am such a researcher.  I want you to take this purchase order to Alessandro Luca, the proprietor of Blue Moon Odds and Ends; he\'ll give you a testing kit.  When you have it, bring it back to me and I\'ll outline your task in detail.' WHERE entry=232; /* title: Errand for Apothecary Zinge */ /* details: The Royal Apothecary Society needs your assistance.  Listen closely, and both of us may profit from my plan.$B$BApothecary Keever in the next room may be... touched... but his research does potentially bear fruit if it were pursued by a clever researcher.  Fortunately, I am such a researcher.  I want you to take this purchase order to Alessandro Luca, the proprietor of Blue Moon Odds and Ends; he\'ll give you a testing kit.  When you have it, bring it back to me and I\'ll outline your task in detail. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Coldridge Valley Mail Delivery' WHERE entry=233; /* title: Coldridge Valley Mail Delivery */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Coldridge Valley Mail Delivery' WHERE entry=234; /* title: Coldridge Valley Mail Delivery */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Caccia a Valtetra',details_loc9='Attenzione, giovani avventurieri! Le terre selvagge di Valtetra vi attendono!$b$bL\'Orda si è insediata nelle terre a nord delle Savane. L\'Avamposto di Troncorotto e l\'Avamposto della Spiaggia di Zoram lottano per portare gloria all\'Orda! Coloro desiderosi di dimostrare il proprio valore possono recarsi laggiù e tentare la fortuna. Una nota: Senani Cuore Tonante all\'Avamposto di Troncorotto, a nord delle Savane, cerca avventurieri che prendano parte a una grande battuta di caccia a Valtetra!',objectives_loc9='Parla con Senani Cuore Tonante all\'Avamposto di Troncorotto nella regione di Valtetra.' WHERE entry=235; /* title: The Ashenvale Hunt */ /* details: Attention, young adventurers!  The wilds of Ashenvale await you!$B$BThe Horde has established a strong presence in the lands north of the Barrens.  Our two outposts - Splintertree Post and the Zoram Strand Outpost - strive to bring glory to the Horde!  Those who would prove themselves should seek out guidance there.  Of note: Senani Thunderheart in Splintertree Post, directly north of the Barrens, seeks adventurers willing to take part in a great hunt of Ashenvale! */ /* objectives: Speak with Senani Thunderheart at Splintertree Post, Ashenvale. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Decisive Strike',details_loc9='Mountaineer Cobbleflint had nothing but good things to say about you, $r.  For that reason I am going to entrust upon you a mission of utmost importance.  We need to keep pressure on the invading Trogg forces until our Dwarven brethren return from the Alliance front.$b$bSet forth into the southern hills and kill 10 Stonesplinter Skullthumpers and 10 Stonesplinter Seers.  Your attacks will buy us some time.  Report back when your mission is complete.' WHERE entry=237; /* title: In Defense of the King\'s Lands */ /* details: Mountaineer Cobbleflint had nothing but good things to say about you, $r.  For that reason I am going to entrust upon you a mission of utmost importance.  We need to keep pressure on the invading Trogg forces until our Dwarven brethren return from the Alliance front.$B$BSet forth into the southern hills and kill 10 Stonesplinter Skullthumpers and 10 Stonesplinter Seers.  Your attacks will buy us some time.  Report back when your mission is complete. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Errand for Apothecary Zinge',details_loc9='The kit is ready, $n.  No doubt that Apothecary Zinge will want this as soon as possible.  Take it to her without delay, and let her know that I will add the cost of the kit to the Society\'s tab.  Also, please extend to her my warmest salutations.$b$bWell, don\'t just stand there.  Such is the life of a simple courier, yes?' WHERE entry=238; /* title: Errand for Apothecary Zinge */ /* details: The kit is ready, $n.  No doubt that Apothecary Zinge will want this as soon as possible.  Take it to her without delay, and let her know that I will add the cost of the kit to the Society\'s tab.  Also, please extend to her my warmest salutations.$B$BWell, don\'t just stand there.  Such is the life of a simple courier, yes? */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Il Presidio Rivombroso ha bisogno d\'aiuto!',details_loc9='Il presidio al confine occidentale ha denunciato un incremento dell\'attività degli Gnoll e dei ladri. Hanno chiesto l\'invio di altri soldati di Roccavento, ma non abbiamo nessuno da mandare!$b$bIl tuo aiuto ci farebbe molto comodo. Va\' a parlare con il Vicesceriffo Rainer al Presidio Rivombroso e senti cosa vuole.$b$bIl presidio si trova lungo la strada a ovest. Lo troverai sulla destra una volta attraversato il ponte sul ruscello.',objectives_loc9='Vai al Presidio Rivombroso e parla con il Vicesceriffo Rainer.' WHERE entry=239; /* title: Westbrook Garrison Needs Help! */ /* details: The Garrison on our western border sends word of increasing gnoll and thief activity.  They\'re requesting we send more Stormwind soldiers... but we just don\'t have any to spare!$B$BIf you can help, we could use it.  Go and speak with Deputy Rainer at the Westbrook Garrison and see what he needs done.$B$BThe Garrison is down the road to the west.  After you cross the bridge over the small brook it will be to the right. */ /* objectives: Go to the Westbrook Garrison and speak with Deputy Rainer. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Into the Field',details_loc9='You will be headed to the Tanaris desert, testing the tissue consistency of the basilisks, scorpids, and hyena native there.  Obtain tissue samples and use them with the testing kit in tow; expect a chunk of the samples to fail.  I need eight acceptable samples of each creature type.$b$bIn addition, the goblins of Gadgetzan have a power source that must be used with this kind of modified kit.  Speak to Chief Engineer Bilgewhizzle and acquire one for the kit.$b$bReturn to me only when you are successful.' WHERE entry=243; /* title: Into the Field */ /* details: You will be headed to the Tanaris desert, testing the tissue consistency of the basilisks, scorpids, and hyena native there.  Obtain tissue samples and use them with the testing kit in tow; expect a chunk of the samples to fail.  I need eight acceptable samples of each creature type.$B$BIn addition, the goblins of Gadgetzan have a power source that must be used with this kind of modified kit.  Speak to Chief Engineer Bilgewhizzle and acquire one for the kit.$B$BReturn to me only when you are successful. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Assessing the Threat',details_loc9='We don\'t have men to spare, but something must be done about those gnolls you reported to me.$b$bScout southern Redridge for gnolls.  Harry them, kill those you can and report back to me with a count of their numbers and an assessment of the threat they present.  You may find those gnolls camped all along the southern road of Redridge.$b$bDo this for the Stormwind Army, $n, and you will be rewarded.' WHERE entry=246; /* title: Assessing the Threat */ /* details: We don\'t have men to spare, but something must be done about those gnolls you reported to me.$B$BScout southern Redridge for gnolls.  Harry them, kill those you can and report back to me with a count of their numbers and an assessment of the threat they present.  You may find those gnolls camped all along the southern road of Redridge.$B$BDo this for the Stormwind Army, $N, and you will be rewarded. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Caccia completata' WHERE entry=247; /* title: The Hunt Completed */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Morganth',details_loc9='After much observation, I have discovered Morganth\'s plans.$b$bHe searches for the Scythe of Elune...and he may have found it!  If he has, then the Redridge Mountains, and the kingdom of Stormwind, will soon feel his dark might.$b$bI am not prepared to pit myself against Morganth, but I fear he must be dealt with now.  So you must enter the Tower of Ilgalar and face Morganth.$b$bDefeat him, and bring me his Pendant of Shadow.  Do this, and the kingdom will owe you much.' WHERE entry=249; /* title: Morganth */ /* details: After much observation, I have discovered Morganth\'s plans.$B$BHe searches for the Scythe of Elune...and he may have found it!  If he has, then the Redridge Mountains, and the kingdom of Stormwind, will soon feel his dark might.$B$BI am not prepared to pit myself against Morganth, but I fear he must be dealt with now.  So you must enter the Tower of Ilgalar and face Morganth.$B$BDefeat him, and bring me his Pendant of Shadow.  Do this, and the kingdom will owe you much. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Sposa dell\'Imbalsamatore' WHERE entry=253; /* title: Bride of the Embalmer */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Mercenaries' WHERE entry=255; /* title: Mercenaries */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ricercato: Chok\'Sul' WHERE entry=256; /* title: Wanted: Chok\'Sul */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Down the Scarlet Path',details_loc9='I will be frank.  We are at war with the Scourge.  It is an evil that corrupts our people and infects our land.  It must be stopped before it overwhelms us and drags our world into shadow.  We of the Scarlet Crusade have sworn to fight the Scourge with body and soul.$b$bIf you are with us, then gather your courage and prove your allegiance--destroy the undead ravagers of Desolace, in the Valley of Bones to the south.$b$bDo this, and the Crusade will embrace you.' WHERE entry=261; /* title: Down the Scarlet Path */ /* details: I will be frank.  We are at war with the Scourge.  It is an evil that corrupts our people and infects our land.  It must be stopped before it overwhelms us and drags our world into shadow.  We of the Scarlet Crusade have sworn to fight the Scourge with body and soul.$B$BIf you are with us, then gather your courage and prove your allegiance--destroy the undead ravagers of Desolace, in the Valley of Bones to the south.$B$BDo this, and the Crusade will embrace you. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Shadowy Figure',details_loc9='I must know who was that skulker in the shadows I saw the night my family was killed!$b$bPlease, $n, you have shown your resourcefulness.  Please find that shadowy figure.  I must learn what secrets he holds!$b$bI do not have clues that you do not already know, but here - take the book you found at my farm.  Perhaps some of the townsfolk can link this book with its owner.' WHERE entry=262; /* title: The Shadowy Figure */ /* details: I must know who was that skulker in the shadows I saw the night my family was killed!$B$BPlease, $N, you have shown your resourcefulness.  Please find that shadowy figure.  I must learn what secrets he holds!$B$BI do not have clues that you do not already know, but here - take the book you found at my farm.  Perhaps some of the townsfolk can link this book with its owner. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Decisive Strike' WHERE entry=263; /* title: In Defense of the King\'s Lands */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Finché morte non ci separi',details_loc9='Maledetto schifoso! Mi lascia per la sua dannata crociata. Perché "la Luce è la cosa più importante che abbiamo contro la minaccia dei non morti".$b$bE i suoi figli, allora?!? E IO?!? Notte dopo notte, l\'ho atteso pazientemente... sempre al secondo posto, dopo i suoi maledetti doveri!$b$bEbbene, ecco a cosa porta la "giustizia", $n! Lui è morto e io sono diventata ciò che combatteva!$b$bPrendi questo pezzo di ferraglia e mettilo sulla sua tomba a Mausolea. Non voglio avere più niente a che fare con questo... né con lui!',objectives_loc9='Metti il Pendente di Clarice sulla Tomba di Yuriv nella Selva Pinargento.' WHERE entry=264; /* title: Until Death Do Us Part */ /* details: Filthy scum! Leaves me for his damn crusade. Because "the Light is the most important thing we have against the threats the undead pose."$B$BWell, what about his children?! What about ME?! Night after night I sat patiently waiting for him... always second to his blasted duty!$B$BWell, witness what "justice" brings you, $N! He\'s dead and I\'m bearing the very thing he was trying to stop!$B$BTake this piece of junk and put it on his tomb at the Sepulcher. I want nothing to do with it anymore... or him! */ /* objectives: Place Clarice\'s Pendant on Yuriv\'s Tomb in Silverpine. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Trogg Threat' WHERE entry=267; /* title: The Trogg Threat */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La flotta maledetta',objectives_loc9='Raggiungi il Porto di Menethil nelle Paludi Grigie e parla con Glorin Frontesalda.' WHERE entry=270; /* title: The Doomed Fleet */ /* objectives: Go to Menethil Harbor in the Wetlands, and speak with Glorin Steelbrow. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Vyrin\'s Revenge' WHERE entry=271; /* title: Vyrin\'s Revenge */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Trial of the Sea Lion',details_loc9='For the second trial, you\'ll need the two halves that make the Pendant of the Sea Lion.  One half draws power from the agility of the sea lion aspect, gliding through water; the other draws power from the incredible endurance of the sea lion aspect.  Druids draw on both these traits equally to embody the aspect of their aquatic form.$b$bSpeak with the locals of Moonglade to learn where the parts may lie, and bring both here to join them together.  Once formed, take the pendant to Dendrite Starblaze.' WHERE entry=272; /* title: Trial of the Sea Lion */ /* details: For the second trial, you\'ll need the two halves that make the Pendant of the Sea Lion.  One half draws power from the agility of the sea lion aspect, gliding through water; the other draws power from the incredible endurance of the sea lion aspect.  Druids draw on both these traits equally to embody the aspect of their aquatic form.$B$BSpeak with the locals of Moonglade to learn where the parts may lie, and bring both here to join them together.  Once formed, take the pendant to Dendrite Starblaze. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rifornimenti per gli scavi',details_loc9='In ogni caso, non è troppo tardi. Va\' pure a cercare Huldar. Non può essere andato molto lontano. Per quanto Miran e Saean siano forti, non riescono a muoversi molto velocemente con quei barili.$b$bStanno percorrendo la strada che costeggia il Loch e che porta dall\'uscita meridionale della città al sito.$b$bNon dovresti avere problemi a trovarli, a meno che non siano già arrivati.',objectives_loc9='Parla con Huldar.' WHERE entry=273; /* title: Resupplying the Excavation */ /* details: It\'s not too late though, you\'re welcome to go look for Huldar. He can\'t have made it very far, strong as they are, Miran and Saean can only move so fast laden down with those barrels.$B$BThey\'re taking the normal route to the site, leaving south out of town and following the curve of the Loch.$B$BShouldn\'t have a problem finding them unless they\'ve already gotten there. */ /* objectives: Speak with Huldar. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Claws from the Deep',details_loc9='Murlocs are crawling out from the deep waters and building their villages on the coastline.  They are harassing our fishers and merchants and must be stopped.$b$bOne of these murlocs, Gobbler, skulks with other bluegill murlocs and harries merchants along the road, always then retreating to the safety of the nearby murloc hovels.  Our merchants are in jeopardy, and we will pay to secure them.$b$bGobbler prowls the river inlet north of here.  Find him, slay his kin, and bring me his head.' WHERE entry=279; /* title: Claws from the Deep */ /* details: Murlocs are crawling out from the deep waters and building their villages on the coastline.  They are harassing our fishers and merchants and must be stopped.$B$BOne of these murlocs, Gobbler, skulks with other bluegill murlocs and harries merchants along the road, always then retreating to the safety of the nearby murloc hovels.  Our merchants are in jeopardy, and we will pay to secure them.$B$BGobbler prowls the river inlet north of here.  Find him, slay his kin, and bring me his head. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Reclaiming Goods',details_loc9='Not long ago a merchant vessel, the Blind Princess, was raided by Murlocs.  Although the ship escaped intact, much of its cargo was dragged overboard by the creatures, including a very valuable statuette of Terenas Menethil.  We want that statuette recovered.$b$bSearch the coastal Murloc hovels for crates, barrels and other evidence of lost cargo.  Find the Menethil Statuette and return it to me.',objectives_loc9='Perlustra le casse e i barili negli accampamenti costieri dei Murloc.' WHERE entry=281; /* title: Reclaiming Goods */ /* details: Not long ago a merchant vessel, the Blind Princess, was raided by Murlocs.  Although the ship escaped intact, much of its cargo was dragged overboard by the creatures, including a very valuable statuette of Terenas Menethil.  We want that statuette recovered.$B$BSearch the coastal Murloc hovels for crates, barrels and other evidence of lost cargo.  Find the Menethil Statuette and return it to me. */ /* objectives: Search the crates and barrels at the coastal Murloc camps. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Search More Hovels',details_loc9='This grouping of Murloc hovels, after a thorough inspection, reveals nothing.$b$b...but you\'re certain that the next clue you find will be fruitful.$b$bOne of the hovels to the north must have the Menethil Statuette!',objectives_loc9='Continua a perlustrare i tuguri dei Murloc alla ricerca della Statuetta di Menethil.' WHERE entry=285; /* title: Search More Hovels */ /* details: This grouping of Murloc hovels, after a thorough inspection, reveals nothing.$B$B...but you\'re certain that the next clue you find will be fruitful.$B$BOne of the hovels to the north must have the Menethil Statuette! */ /* objectives: Continue searching the Murloc hovels for the Menethil Statuette. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Covo dei Mantogelido',details_loc9='Sono indietro con il mio rapporto, $n, e mi serve il tuo aiuto. Ho appena scoperto dove sono rintanati i Troll, ma sono talmente tanti che ho paura ad affrontarli.$b$bEcco quello che devi fare... vai nella caverna, dai un\'occhiata in giro, uccidi qualche Troll e poi torna da me.$b$bPrendi la strada a nord fuori da Kharanos. Una volta raggiunto il ponte, segui il fiume gelato a ovest fino ad arrivare al Lago di Ghiacciospesso. Sull\'argine a ovest c\'è Borgo Luppolo. Il loro covo si trova a sud-ovest del villaggio.',objectives_loc9='Esplora il Covo dei Mantogelido e uccidi 5 Cacciatori di Teste Mantogelido per Senir Barbabianca a Kharanos.' WHERE entry=287; /* title: Frostmane Hold */ /* details: I\'m behind on my report, and could use your help, $n. I just managed to find where the trolls are holed up, but I saw so many trolls, I was afraid to go in.$B$BHere\'s what I need... Go down to the cave, poke around inside, kill a few of the trolls, then come back here.$B$BTake the road north out of Kharanos, when you get to the bridge, follow the frozen river west until you reach Iceflow Lake. You\'ll find Brewnall Village on the west bank. The Hold is southwest of the village. */ /* objectives: Explore Frostmane Hold, and kill 5 Frostmane Headhunters for Senir Whitebeard in Kharanos. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Third Fleet',details_loc9='I was once First Mate on the Wave Mistress, ship-of-the-line in the Kul Tiras Third Fleet.  The Doomed Fleet.  Doomed, for on its last voyage the fleet was attacked  by Red Dragons.  Dragons controlled by Orcs!$b$bWe didn\'t stand a chance against that dragonfire...and our fleet was burned and sunk off this here coast.  I\'m the sole survivor of those poor vessels...$b$b...Oh, my head hammers and pounds!  I\'ll need a fresh drink if I\'m to get a handle on this hangover and continue my tale.' WHERE entry=288; /* title: The Third Fleet */ /* details: I was once First Mate on the Wave Mistress, ship-of-the-line in the Kul Tiras Third Fleet.  The Doomed Fleet.  Doomed, for on its last voyage the fleet was attacked  by Red Dragons.  Dragons controlled by Orcs!$B$BWe didn\'t stand a chance against that dragonfire...and our fleet was burned and sunk off this here coast.  I\'m the sole survivor of those poor vessels...$B$B...Oh, my head hammers and pounds!  I\'ll need a fresh drink if I\'m to get a handle on this hangover and continue my tale. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='I rapporti',details_loc9='Eccellente! Consegna i miei rapporti al Senatore Barin Pietrarossa. Ti avverto, è un tipo burbero. Non lasciarti impressionare. Si trova a Forgiardente, nella stanza dove si riunisce la corte di Re Magni.$b$bPer raggiungere Forgiardente prendi la strada a nord fuori da Kharanos, attraversa il ponte e segui il sentiero a est che si arrampica sul fianco della montagna. Vedrai dei grossi stendardi ai lati della strada.$b$bA proposito... ti sarei grato se evitassi di dire che mi hai aiutato. Non vorrei che pensassero che non mi impegni abbastanza.',objectives_loc9='Consegna i Rapporti di Senir al Senatore Barin Pietrarossa nella città di Forgiardente.' WHERE entry=291; /* title: The Reports */ /* details: Excellent! Take my report to Senator Barin Redstone. He\'s a sour type, so don\'t let his less-than-sunny disposition get to you. He\'s in Ironforge, in the chamber where King Magni holds court.$B$BDon\'t know the way to Ironforge? Take the road out of Kharanos north, cross the bridge, then follow the road east--there are large banners flanking the road--up the mountainside.$B$BBy the way, if you might avoid mentioning how you assisted me? Can\'t let them think I\'m not working hard out here, you know? */ /* objectives: Deliver Senir\'s report to Senator Barin Redstone in Ironforge. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Cleansing the Eye',details_loc9='I can\'t lift the curse from the Eye of Paleth.  The Eyes were crafted by Human Priests, so you\'ll have to go to Stormwind to find someone who can help you.  Speak with Archbishop Benedictus.  He is head of the Cathedral of Light in Stormwind.  He can help.$b$bI hope, for your sake.' WHERE entry=293; /* title: Cleansing the Eye */ /* details: I can\'t lift the curse from the Eye of Paleth.  The Eyes were crafted by Human Priests, so you\'ll have to go to Stormwind to find someone who can help you.  Speak with Archbishop Benedictus.  He is head of the Cathedral of Light in Stormwind.  He can help.$B$BI hope, for your sake. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Gathering Idols' WHERE entry=297; /* title: Gathering Idols */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rapporto sui Progressi degli scavi',details_loc9='Devo inviare un Rapporto sui Progressi a Thelsamar. Quello, e una nota di sollecito per la mia richiesta di altra polvere esplosiva! Ecco il Rapporto! Portalo a Jern Elmocorno. È il nostro contatto locale a Thelsamar.$b$bNon è un incarico difficile, ma dev\'essere portato a termine.',objectives_loc9='Porta il Rapporto sui Progressi di Ferrocollo a Jern Elmocorno a Thelsamar.' WHERE entry=298; /* title: Excavation Progress Report */ /* details: I need a progress report sent to Thelsamar - a progress report, and a restatement of my request for more blastpowder!  Here\'s the report.  Take it to Jern Hornhelm.  He\'s our local contact in Thelsamar.$B$BIt\'s not a difficult task, but it must be done. */ /* objectives: Bring Ironband\'s Progress Report to Jern Hornhelm in Thelsamar. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Uncovering the Past',details_loc9='Just before the invasion I uncovered a large tablet called the Goaz Stone.  The translated text breaks off in 4 places.  The text speaks of a "divine plan" and a "doomed prophecy."$b$bI fear we are running out of time.  I am too old to go down and brave those beasts.  But you are strong.$b$bScour the excavation site and uncover the 4 missing tablet fragments: Ados, Modr, Golm and Neru.  Search for them in ancient artifacts or where the soil is loose.  Bring them to me so I can begin unlocking the mystery!' WHERE entry=299; /* title: Uncovering the Past */ /* details: Just before the invasion I uncovered a large tablet called the Goaz Stone.  The translated text breaks off in 4 places.  The text speaks of a "divine plan" and a "doomed prophecy."$B$BI fear we are running out of time.  I am too old to go down and brave those beasts.  But you are strong.$B$BScour the excavation site and uncover the 4 missing tablet fragments: Ados, Modr, Golm and Neru.  Search for them in ancient artifacts or where the soil is loose.  Bring them to me so I can begin unlocking the mystery! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rapporto a Forgiardente',details_loc9='Mi serve l\'approvazione per fornire a Ferrocollo altra polvere esplosiva. Dovrai portare il suo Rapporto alla sede della Lega degli Esploratori a Forgiardente.$b$bEcco. Dallo al Prospettore Piccatonante. E non scordare di abbassarti dopo averglielo consegnato. Piccatonante è una testa calda e non gli farà piacere sentire dei lenti progressi negli scavi di Ferrocollo.$b$bTroverai Piccatonante al Consiglio degli Esploratori.',objectives_loc9='Porta il Rapporto sui Progressi di Ferrocollo al Prospettore Piccatonante.' WHERE entry=301; /* title: Report to Ironforge */ /* details: We\'ll need approval to get Ironband more blastpowder. You\'ll have to take his report to the Explorers\' League headquarters in Ironforge.$B$BHere\'s the report. Give it to Prospector Stormpike, and don\'t forget to duck after you deliver it. Stormpike is hotheaded, and he won\'t be happy to hear of Ironband\'s slow progress at the site.$B$BYou\'ll find Stormpike in the Assembly of Explorers. */ /* objectives: Take Ironband\'s Progress Report to Prospector Stormpike. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Polvere per Ferrocollo',details_loc9='Se a Ferrocollo serve polvere esplosiva, allora, nel nome di Magni, l\'avrà! Ho appena mandato la lettera di approvazione con un messaggero a Jern Elmocorno. Preparerà la polvere esplosiva e altri rifornimenti da portare a Ferrocollo.$b$bUn\'altra cosa: voglio che verifichi personalmente che il carico di polvere esplosiva arrivi a destinazione. L\'ultimo carico non è giunto, quindi occhi aperti e fa\' attenzione.',objectives_loc9='Parla con Jern Elmocorno a Thelsamar.' WHERE entry=302; /* title: Powder to Ironband */ /* details: If Ironband still needs blastpowder, then by Magni he\'ll have it!  I sent the approval on ahead with a messenger to Jern Hornhelm in Thelsamar.  He\'ll prepare the powder and other supplies to take to Ironband.$B$BAnd one more thing: I want you to personally see that the shipment of powder reaches its destination.  The last one didn\'t, so keep your mind sharp and your eyes open. */ /* objectives: Speak with Jern Hornhelm in Thelsamar. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Dark Iron War',details_loc9='War rages both home and abroad.  While mighty Dwarven soldiers give their lives in far off territories in the name of the Alliance, our own lands fall prey to the evil deeds of the Dark Iron Dwarves.  They laid waste to the Thandol Span.  Dun Modr fell soon after.$b$bWe need you to gather force and push the front back.  If you can kill 10 Dark Iron Dwarves, 5 Tunnelers, 5 Saboteurs and 5 Demolitionists, the reserve might arrive in time to finish the drive.$b$bNow make haste!' WHERE entry=303; /* title: The Dark Iron War */ /* details: War rages both home and abroad.  While mighty Dwarven soldiers give their lives in far off territories in the name of the Alliance, our own lands fall prey to the evil deeds of the Dark Iron Dwarves.  They laid waste to the Thandol Span.  Dun Modr fell soon after.$B$BWe need you to gather force and push the front back.  If you can kill 10 Dark Iron Dwarves, 5 Tunnelers, 5 Saboteurs and 5 Demolitionists, the reserve might arrive in time to finish the drive.$B$BNow make haste! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='In Search of The Excavation Team',details_loc9='Oh my, you must be the scout Longbraid said he would send!  You cannot imagine how worried I have been.$b$bMy wife, Merrin, has been sending me letters each week for the past month.  She is part of the Whelgar Excavation team.  But it has been nearly two weeks since her last correspondence.  Surely something is wrong!$b$bLongbraid said that he would send a scout to check up on things if we did not hear from the team soon.  I assume that scout is you, $n.  Find Merrin at the excavation site to the east!' WHERE entry=305; /* title: In Search of The Excavation Team */ /* details: Oh my, you must be the scout Longbraid said he would send!  You cannot imagine how worried I have been.$B$BMy wife, Merrin, has been sending me letters each week for the past month.  She is part of the Whelgar Excavation team.  But it has been nearly two weeks since her last correspondence.  Surely something is wrong!$B$BLongbraid said that he would send a scout to check up on things if we did not hear from the team soon.  I assume that scout is you, $N.  Find Merrin at the excavation site to the east! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='In Search of The Excavation Team' WHERE entry=306; /* title: In Search of The Excavation Team */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Filthy Paws',details_loc9='The Silver Stream Mine to the east ran dry long ago. It was converted by the Miners\' League into a storage depot, but now Kobolds have moved in, putting their filthy paws on good, Dwarven tools!$b$bWe\'ll root out those vermin soon enough, but the League wants someone to get their gear out of the mine before we warriors tromp in there and break things.  It\'ll be a tough delve - you might want cohorts at your side.$b$bThe gear is stored in Miners\' League Crates throughout the mine.  Good luck.' WHERE entry=307; /* title: Filthy Paws */ /* details: The Silver Stream Mine to the east ran dry long ago.  It was converted by the Miners\' League into a storage depot, but now Kobolds have moved in, putting their filthy paws on good, Dwarven tools!$B$BWe\'ll root out those vermin soon enough, but the League wants someone to get their gear out of the mine before we warriors tromp in there and break things.  It\'ll be a tough delve - you might want cohorts at your side.$B$BThe gear is stored in Miners\' League Crates throughout the mine.  Good luck. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Proteggete il carico' WHERE entry=309; /* title: Protecting the Shipment */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Odiati rivali',details_loc9='Ammetto che quei Birratuono servono roba buona, ma devono imparare che la loro birra non è l\'unica degna di essere bevuta! Forse tu puoi aiutarmi a farglielo capire...$b$bPrendi questo Barile di Ustionante dei Maltorzo. Introduciti nella cantina della Distilleria Birratuono a Kharanos e mettilo al posto di uno dei loro barili di Birra del Tuono. Vedremo se i loro clienti apprezzano di più la loro birra o la mia!$b$bSe i barili dovessero essere sorvegliati, trova un modo per distrarre la guardia...',objectives_loc9='Sostituisci un Barile di Birra del Tuono con un Barile di Ustionante dei Maltorzo nella cantina della Distilleria Birratuono.' WHERE entry=310; /* title: Bitter Rivals */ /* details: I have to admit, those Thunderbrews make some good drinks.  But they need to learn that theirs isn\'t the only decent brew!  Maybe you can help me teach them that lesson...$B$BHere, take this barrel of Barleybrew Scalder.  Sneak into the basement of the Thunderbrew Distillery in Kharanos and switch it with one of their barrels of Thunder Ale.  Then we\'ll see how their patrons like my brew over theirs!$B$BAnd if the barrels are guarded, then you might have to distract the guard ... */ /* objectives: In the basement of the Thunderbrew Distillery in Kharanos, replace a barrel of Thunder Ale with a Barrel of Barleybrew Scalder. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ritorno da Marleth',details_loc9='<Dopo aver introdotto il Barile di Ustionante dei Maltorzo nella cantina della Distilleria Birratuono, prendi un Barile di Birra del Tuono come prova...>',objectives_loc9='Porta il Barile di Birra del Tuono a Marleth Maltorzo nel villaggio di Borgo Luppolo.' WHERE entry=311; /* title: Return to Marleth */ /* details: Having inserted a barrel of Marleth\'s Scalder in the Kharanos Distillery\'s cellar, you grab a barrel of Thunder Ale as proof of the deed... */ /* objectives: Bring the barrel of Thunder Ale to Marleth Barleybrew at the Brewnall Village. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Le provviste rubate di MacGrann della Tundra',details_loc9='Avevo preparato della carne essiccata per l\'inverno e l\'avevo messa nel congelatore, in modo che gli orsi non potessero mangiarla. Mentre ero a caccia di cervi, però, il Vecchio Barbagelo ha rubato il congelatore. Non credo che riuscirà a scassinare la serratura in torio. D\'altro canto, se io non riavrò indietro la mia carne, morirò di fame.$b$bForse tu puoi aiutarmi a recuperare le mie provviste. Io non riuscirei mai a entrare e uscire da quella caverna abbastanza in fretta con le gambe tozze che mi ritrovo.',objectives_loc9='Recupera la carne essiccata di MacGrann della Tundra dal congelatore rubato nella grotta del Vecchio Barbagelo.' WHERE entry=312; /* title: Tundra MacGrann\'s Stolen Stash */ /* details: I had a month\'s worth of dried meats salted and locked away for the cold season.  Kept it locked so the bears wouldn\'t get it!  But while I was off hunting deer, that beast, Old Icebeard, made off with the meat locker.  He won\'t be able to smash through that Thorium though.  But I\'ll starve if I can\'t get my meats back.$B$BYou seem a bit more stealthy than me.  Perhaps you can retrieve my stash?  I\'ll never make it in and out of that cave fast enough with this bum leg of mine. */ /* objectives: Retrieve Tundra MacGrann\'s dried meats from the stolen meat locker in Old Icebeard\'s cave. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Tana Selvaggia' WHERE entry=313; /* title: The Grizzled Den */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Proteggere il gregge' WHERE entry=314; /* title: Protecting the Herd */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La birra scura perfetta' WHERE entry=315; /* title: The Perfect Stout */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rifornire il Vaporizzatore Meccanico',details_loc9='Sto preparando una missione per la Brigata d\'Assedio. Sarà una cosa lunga e devo rifornire il Vaporizzatore Meccanico per un mese. Mentre Grigliafredda lavora al mio carro, potresti andare a caccia per me?$b$bMi servono delle pellicce per i letti e della carne di cinghiale da mangiare. La carne la puoi ottenere dai cinghiali e la pelliccia dagli orsi... si trovano entrambi nei campi innevati a sud della Tana Selvaggia.',objectives_loc9='Ottieni 4 Tranci di Carne di Cinghiale e 2 Pellicce d\'Orso Folte, e consegna tutto al Pilota Gridapietra nello Scalo di Grigliafredda.' WHERE entry=317; /* title: Stocking Jetsteam */ /* details: I\'m preparing to start a mission for the Siege Brigade.  It\'s a long one, and I need to stock Jetsteam with a month\'s worth of supplies.  So while Steelgrill is working on my tank, can you do some hunting for me?$B$BI\'ll need some fur for bedding, and boar meat for food.  You can get meat from boars and fur from the bears... you can find them both in the snow fields south of the Grizzled Den. */ /* objectives: Gather 4 Chunks of Boar Meat and 2 Thick Bear Furs, and deliver them to Pilot Bellowfiz at Steelgrill\'s Depot. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Evershine',details_loc9='Rejold Maltorzo si diverte a creare nuovi tipi di birre. Alcune gli riescono bene, altre meno, e altre ancora... be\', stenderebbero anche il più resistente dei Nani.$b$bRejold vive a Borgo Luppolo, a ovest di Kharanos. Voglio uno dei suoi prodotti, la Trinciabudella. Mi aiuterà a scaldarmi mentre sono fuori in strada al freddo.$b$bInoltre, quella roba è talmente forte che posso usarla anche per alimentare la fornace del Vaporizzatore Meccanico! Questa tattica mi ha permesso di tirarmi fuori dai guai in più di una situazione.',objectives_loc9='Procurati una Cassa di Trinciabudella da Rejold Maltorzo a Borgo Luppolo.' WHERE entry=318; /* title: Evershine */ /* details: Rejold Barleybrew experiments with his brews.  Some of them taste good, some bad, and some...well, some will lay all but the stoutest dwarf flat.$B$BHe lives at Brewnall Village, west of Kharanos, and one of his drinks, Evershine, is what I want.  It\'ll help keep me warm while I\'m on the cold road.$B$BAnd...the blessed stuff burns so hot I can throw it in Jetsteam\'s furnace for a burst of power!  That little tactic has gotten me out of more than one tight spot. */ /* objectives: Get a cask of Evershine from Rejold Barleybrew in Brewnall Village. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Un favore in cambio di Trinciabudella',details_loc9='Ho giusto una Cassa di Trinciabudella disponibile, ma te la darò solo se mi farai un favore. Borgo Luppolo ha bisogno d\'aiuto con gli animali selvaggi che vagano qui vicino... a volte anche troppo.$b$bNessun Nano che si rispetti ha paura di orsi, leopardi o cinghiali, ma se tu potessi sbarazzarti di quegli animali per noi, avremmo più tempo da dedicare alle nostre creazioni e alla nostra birra.',objectives_loc9='Uccidi 6 Orsi dalle Zampe di Ghiaccio, 8 Cinghiali Anziani delle Rupi e 8 Leopardi delle Nevi, poi torna da Rejold Maltorzo a Borgo Luppolo.' WHERE entry=319; /* title: A Favor for Evershine */ /* details: I have a cask of Evershine handy, but...can you do me a favor?  Brewnall village could use a hand against the wild animals that wander the nearby snows.  Sometimes they wander close.$B$BWe\'re not afraid of these bears and cats and boars - no self respecting dwarf would be - but if you can take care of those animals for us, then we\'d have more time for our crafting and brewing. */ /* objectives: Kill 6 Ice Claw Bears, 8 Elder Crag Boars, and 8 Snow Leopards, and then return to Rejold Barleybrew in Brewnall Village. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ritorno da Gridapietra',details_loc9='Ecco la tua Cassa di Trinciabudella, $n. E grazie ancora per aver ucciso quelle bestie.',objectives_loc9='Consegna la Cassa di Trinciabudella al Pilota Gridapietra nello Scalo di Grigliafredda.' WHERE entry=320; /* title: Return to Bellowfiz */ /* details: Here\'s your cask of Evershine, $N.  And again, thank you for the hunting earlier. */ /* objectives: Give the cask of Evershine to Pilot Bellowfiz at Steelgrill\'s Depot. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Lightforge Iron',details_loc9='The shipwrecks off the shore here are the doomed Third Fleet of Kul\'Tiras, burned and sunk by Red Dragons during the last Great War.$b$bThe Fleet hailed from Lordaeron, but one ship, an Elvish Destroyer: Flying Osprey, was with it.  It was shipping a load of Lightforge Iron and joined the Third Fleet for protection.  Ironic that it sunk to the same dragons...$b$bEnough history.  The Flying Osprey is wrecked to the south of Menethil Harbor.  If you find the Lightforge Iron there, bring it to me.' WHERE entry=321; /* title: Lightforge Iron */ /* details: The shipwrecks off the shore here are the doomed Third Fleet of Kul\'Tiras, burned and sunk by Red Dragons during the last Great War.$B$BThe Fleet hailed from Lordaeron, but one ship, an Elvish Destroyer: Flying Osprey, was with it.  It was shipping a load of Lightforge Iron and joined the Third Fleet for protection.  Ironic that it sunk to the same dragons...$B$BEnough history.  The Flying Osprey is wrecked to the south of Menethil Harbor.  If you find the Lightforge Iron there, bring it to me. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Proving Your Worth',details_loc9='Morbent Fel is a necromancer, and an ally to the dark riders.  I would pit you against the power of Morbent Fel, but I will not send you against that vile fiend without first knowing your strength.$b$bYou have already proven your bravery to me, but if you truly wish to face the necromancer, then you must now prove your skill against his minions.' WHERE entry=323; /* title: Proving Your Worth */ /* details: Morbent Fel is a necromancer, and an ally to the dark riders.  I would pit you against the power of Morbent Fel, but I will not send you against that vile fiend without first knowing your strength.$B$BYou have already proven your bravery to me, but if you truly wish to face the necromancer, then you must now prove your skill against his minions. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Armi in pugno',details_loc9='Ecco l\'arma contro il demonio di cui parlavi. Hai tutto ciò di cui hai bisogno, $n. Ti auguro buona fortuna, e non vedo l\'ora di sentire i gloriosi racconti delle tue gesta!',objectives_loc9='Porta l\'Anatema di Morbent a Sven a Boscovespro.' WHERE entry=325; /* title: Armed and Ready */ /* details: Here is the weapon against the fiend of which you spoke.  You\'re all ready, $N.  Best of luck to you, and I look forward to your tale of glory! */ /* objectives: Bring Morbent\'s Bane to Sven in Duskwood. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Spy Revealed!',details_loc9='Among the valuables of the strongbox is a muddy, scribbled note.  Although barely legible, it looks to be an itinerary for Private Thorsen.  It details his patrol routes, who he speaks with and how he spends his time with the rebels.  It\'s signed with only one letter: -M.$b$bBut whoever wrote this note must have stayed very close to Thorsen.  Whoever wrote this note is the traitor within the rebel camp.' WHERE entry=329; /* title: The Spy Revealed! */ /* details: Among the valuables of the strongbox is a muddy, scribbled note.  Although barely legible, it looks to be an itinerary for Private Thorsen.  It details his patrol routes, who he speaks with and how he spends his time with the rebels.  It\'s signed with only one letter: -M.$B$BBut whoever wrote this note must have stayed very close to Thorsen.  Whoever wrote this note is the traitor within the rebel camp. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Report to Doren',details_loc9='Did Lieutenant Doren want you to report back to him with that patrol information?' WHERE entry=331; /* title: Report to Doren */ /* details: Did Lieutenant Doren want you to report back to him with that patrol information? */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Pubblicità della bottega del vino',objectives_loc9='Vai all\'Enoteca dei Gallina e consegna a Susetta Gallina il Buono per il Vino per ricevere una bottiglia di vino gratis.' WHERE entry=332; /* title: Wine Shop Advert */ /* objectives: Go to the Gallina Winery, and bring Suzetta Gallina the Wine Ticket for a free bottle of wine. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Harlan ha bisogno di un rifornimento',details_loc9='Gli affari vanno benissimo ultimamente. Sembra che tutti stiano comprando armature e vestiti pesanti, come se prevedessero l\'arrivo di una stagione rigida...$b$bMa queste sono preoccupazioni che riguardano il futuro. Oggi il problema è che sto terminando i tessuti lavorati. Ho bisogno di un altro carico dal nostro fornitore.$b$bSe potessi consegnare questa richiesta a Rema Schneider al Sarto del Canale, Tutto su Misura, te ne sarei grato.',objectives_loc9='Vai dal Sarto del Canale, Tutto su Misura e consegna a Rema Schneider la Richiesta di Stoffa da parte di Harlan Bagley.' WHERE entry=333; /* title: Harlan Needs a Resupply */ /* details: We\'ve been doing a lot of business lately.  It seems like everyone is buying armor and sturdy clothes.  Almost like they expect a cold, harsh season ahead...$B$BBut those are future worries.  My worry today is that I\'m running out of knitted clothing to sell.  I need another load from our supplier.$B$BIf you can take this request to Rema Schneider at the Canal Tailor and Fit Shop, I\'d be most grateful. */ /* objectives: Go to the Canal Tailor Shop and bring Rema Schneider the Cloth Request from Harlan Bagley. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Un pacco per Thurman',details_loc9='Mio figlio Thurman lavora come apprendista da Larson Vende Moda, nel Quartiere dei Maghi. Oggi aveva fretta e si è dimenticato aghi e forbici. So che <un/una> prode $c come te sarà certamente <impegnato/impegnata> in qualche importante missione, ma senza queste cose Thurman non può lavorare!$b$bTi prego, $n. Puoi portare a mio figlio i suoi strumenti da cucito? Larson Vende Moda è una delle due botteghe di vestiti nel Quartiere dei Maghi. È quello più all\'interno, vicino alla Torre del Mago.',objectives_loc9='Vai da Larson Vende Moda nel Quartiere dei Maghi di Roccavento e consegna a Thurman Schneider i suoi Strumenti da Cucito.' WHERE entry=334; /* title: Package for Thurman */ /* details: My son Thurman is an apprentice at the Larson Clothiers, in the Mage\'s Quarter.  He was in a hurry today and forgot his shears and needles.  I know a great $C like you must have important tasks at hand, but without his tools Thurman can\'t do his apprentice work!$B$BPlease, $N.  Can you take my son\'s sewing kit to him?  Larson Clothiers is one of two clothing shops in the Mage\'s Quarter - it\'s the one deeper in, near the Mage\'s Tower. */ /* objectives: Go to the Larson Clothiers in the Stormwind Mage Quarter, and give Thurman Schneider his Sewing Kit. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Una nobile mistura',details_loc9='Ser Wishock sta provocando un certo trambusto nella Casata dei Nobili. È stato informato della nostra piccola "attività" quaggiù e sta preparando un\'indagine approfondita. Ho un piano per tenerlo "occupato", ma avrò bisogno del tuo aiuto.$b$bC\'è un fiore che cresce nel Giardino di Stalvan, alla periferia di Borgoscuro. Questo piccolo fiore bianco è noto come Lacrima di Tilloa. Avrò bisogno anche di una Radice Muschiata, che si trova solo alla fine delle cascate, in profondità sotto la Diga di Pietrasalda nelle Paludi Grigie.',objectives_loc9='Zardeth Graffionero ti ha chiesto di portargli una Lacrima di Tilloa da Borgoscuro e una Radice Muschiata dalle Paludi Grigie.' WHERE entry=335; /* title: A Noble Brew */ /* details: Lord Wishock is causing quite a stir amongst the House of Nobles.  He was made aware of our little "establishment" down here and is lobbying for a full investigation.  I have a plan to keep Wishock "preoccupied," but I\'ll need your help. $B$BThere is a flower growing in the Garden of Stalvan on the outskirts of Darkshire.  This small white flower is known as the Tear of Tilloa.  I will also need a Musquash Root, found only at the very base of the falls far beneath the Stonewrought Dam in the Wetlands. */ /* objectives: Zardeth the Black Claw wants you to bring him a Tear of Tilloa from Darkshire and a Musquash Root from the Wetlands. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Una nobile mistura' WHERE entry=336; /* title: A Noble Brew */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='An Old History Book',details_loc9='Although the cover of this book is marred by scratches and caked with mud, the words "The History of Stormwind" can still be read along its spine.  Upon opening the book, the seal of the Stormwind Library is clearly stamped on the book\'s first page.$b$bIt looks like someone checked out this book, and never returned it...' WHERE entry=337; /* title: An Old History Book */ /* details: Although the cover of this book is marred by scratches and caked with mud, the words "The History of Stormwind" can still be read along its spine.  Upon opening the book, the seal of the Stormwind Library is clearly stamped on the book\'s first page.$B$BIt looks like someone checked out this book, and never returned it... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Le Colline Verdi di Stranglethorn',details_loc9='Master Nesingwary will be so upset if he finds out!$b$bHe trusted me to proofread the manuscript of his novel, The Green Hills of Stranglethorn.  Everything was going well, but a large gust of wind blew through the camp and scattered the pages everywhere!$b$bI was able to gather most of the pages but many are still strewn about the jungle.  Collect the pages to complete each of the four chapters.$b$bI will help you organize them.  Return the chapters to me once you have all four.' WHERE entry=338; /* title: The Green Hills of Stranglethorn */ /* details: Master Nesingwary will be so upset if he finds out!$B$BHe trusted me to proofread the manuscript of his novel, The Green Hills of Stranglethorn.  Everything was going well, but a large gust of wind blew through the camp and scattered the pages everywhere!$B$BI was able to gather most of the pages but many are still strewn about the jungle.  Collect the pages to complete each of the four chapters.$B$BI will help you organize them.  Return the chapters to me once you have all four. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Chapter I',details_loc9='Chapter I was quite riveting!  Master Nesingwary sets the backdrop for the story and makes mention of his hunting companions, including me! $b$bBut that\'s besides the point.  Let me see which pages are still missing.  It seems pages 1, 4, 6 and 8 are still out there somewhere in the jungle!' WHERE entry=339; /* title: Chapter I */ /* details: Chapter I was quite riveting!  Master Nesingwary sets the backdrop for the story and makes mention of his hunting companions, including me! $B$BBut that\'s besides the point.  Let me see which pages are still missing.  It seems pages 1, 4, 6 and 8 are still out there somewhere in the jungle! */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Chapter III',details_loc9='Chapter III was my favorite.  It tells of Sir Erlgadin and Lady Rouack\'s first kill with a dwarven rifle.  And the end of Chapter III, why, such a cliffhanger!  $b$bLooks to me as though we still need pages 18, 20, 21 and 24 to finish the chapter.  Those pages are out there somewhere. . .' WHERE entry=341; /* title: Chapter III */ /* details: Chapter III was my favorite.  It tells of Sir Erlgadin and Lady Rouack\'s first kill with a dwarven rifle.  And the end of Chapter III, why, such a cliffhanger!  $B$BLooks to me as though we still need pages 18, 20, 21 and 24 to finish the chapter.  Those pages are out there somewhere. . . */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Speaking of Fortitude',details_loc9='I\'m giving a speech on the Fortitude of the Spirit, and I\'d like to recite passages from a particular book on metallurgy - "The Stresses of Iron."  A copy of this book should be in the Royal Library, within Stormwind Keep.  Can you retrieve it for me?  If so, then may the blessings of the Light be with you!$b$bThe Royal Library is very large, but the head librarian, Milton Sheaf, knows each shelf like it was his own son.  Speak to him, he\'ll retrieve the book for you.' WHERE entry=343; /* title: Speaking of Fortitude */ /* details: I\'m giving a speech on the Fortitude of the Spirit, and I\'d like to recite passages from a particular book on metallurgy - "The Stresses of Iron."  A copy of this book should be in the Royal Library, within Stormwind Keep.  Can you retrieve it for me?  If so, then may the blessings of the Light be with you!$B$BThe Royal Library is very large, but the head librarian, Milton Sheaf, knows each shelf like it was his own son.  Speak to him, he\'ll retrieve the book for you. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Brother Paxton',details_loc9='The Stresses of Iron?  Yes, I know the book.  Quite a good one, written by the Dwarven miner Margulf Blaggon a few decades ago.  He spent most his time deep in the mountains of Khaz Modan, digging ore.  Smart fellow!$b$bBut where was I?  Oh yes, the Stresses of Iron!  I\'m afraid the book was moved to the Northshire Abbey.  The caretaker of the Abbey\'s library, Brother Paxton, wanted to make a copy of the book for his own shelves.$b$bBut that was months ago.  I wonder why it\'s taking him so long...' WHERE entry=344; /* title: Brother Paxton */ /* details: The Stresses of Iron?  Yes, I know the book.  Quite a good one, written by the Dwarven miner Margulf Blaggon a few decades ago.  He spent most his time deep in the mountains of Khaz Modan, digging ore.  Smart fellow!$B$BBut where was I?  Oh yes, the Stresses of Iron!  I\'m afraid the book was moved to the Northshire Abbey.  The caretaker of the Abbey\'s library, Brother Paxton, wanted to make a copy of the book for his own shelves.$B$BBut that was months ago.  I wonder why it\'s taking him so long... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Ink Supplies' WHERE entry=345; /* title: Ink Supplies */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rethban Ore',details_loc9='Rethban Ore is named after the man who first found it, Bart Rethban.  When smelted it\'s not as strong as iron, but its ore has a dark, flat color that some scribes use in their dyes.  It can be found in the Rethban Caverns, north of here.$b$bWe usually have some in stock, but we\'re too busy preparing for Orc attacks to gather any.  And besides...Redridge Gnolls are now living in the Rethban Caverns and their Drudgers are gathering the ore themselves.$b$bSo if you need some, you\'ll have to get it yourself.' WHERE entry=347; /* title: Rethban Ore */ /* details: Rethban Ore is named after the man who first found it, Bart Rethban.  When smelted it\'s not as strong as iron, but its ore has a dark, flat color that some scribes use in their dyes.  It can be found in the Rethban Caverns, north of here.$B$BWe usually have some in stock, but we\'re too busy preparing for Orc attacks to gather any.  And besides...Redridge Gnolls are now living in the Rethban Caverns and their Drudgers are gathering the ore themselves.$B$BSo if you need some, you\'ll have to get it yourself. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Stranglethorn Fever',details_loc9='Sick...so...very s-s-sick....$b$b...have contracted Stranglethorn Fever...deadly v-v-virus...$b$b...only cure...is...is...to eat the heart of M-m-m-m-mokk the Savage...elusive white beast...$b$b...Witch doctor Unbagwa...only one who can s-s-summon....$b$b...seek Unbagwa in hidden cave on southern cape...$b$b...hurry...dying...dying....' WHERE entry=348; /* title: Stranglethorn Fever */ /* details: Sick...so...very s-s-sick....$B$B...have contracted Stranglethorn Fever...deadly v-v-virus...$B$B...only cure...is...is...to eat the heart of M-m-m-m-mokk the Savage...elusive white beast...$B$B...Witch doctor Unbagwa...only one who can s-s-summon....$B$B...seek Unbagwa in hidden cave on southern cape...$B$B...hurry...dying...dying.... */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Stranglethorn Fever' WHERE entry=349; /* title: Stranglethorn Fever */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Trova OOX-17/TN!',details_loc9='<Hai scoperto uno strano strumento metallico a forma di uovo. Trafficando con le manopole, lo rimetti in funzione. L\'uovo si apre, diventando una specie di macchinario robotico dei Goblin! Dall\'interno, proviene una voce gracchiante:>$b$b"Mi chiamo Oglethorpe, e il mio robot teleguidato è sparito! Se me lo restituirai, ti ricompenserò! Ti prego di portare questo trasmettitore d\'emergenza al robot. Ottimo, ti ho inviato le coordinate! Si è schiantato nei pressi dell\'Abisso Golaperta a Tanaris!"',objectives_loc9='Porta il trasmettitore d\'emergenza al Robot Teleguidato di Oglethorpe.' WHERE entry=351; /* title: Find OOX-17/TN! */ /* details: You have uncovered some sort of strange, egg-shaped device made from metal.  Fiddling with one of its knobs springs the egg to life, as it opens up into some sort of gnomish robotic contraption!  A voice from inside the robotic egg crackles to life.$B$B"The name\'s Oglethorpe, and my homing robot has gone missing!  I will reward you for its recovery!  Please take this beacon to the robot.  Excellent, I now have computed the coordinates for you!  It crashed near the Gaping Chasm in Tanaris!" */ /* objectives: Bring the distress beacon to Oglethorpe\'s homing robot. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='La consegna di Piccatonante',details_loc9='I Piccatonante sono un rispettato clan di Nani, noti per i loro gusti raffinati ed esigenti. Quindi non c\'è da stupirsi che Gringer Piccatonante, un Montanaro di Forgiardente, mi abbia ordinato di forgiargli un\'arma.$b$bL\'arma è finita, ma... il Montanaro Piccatonante è distante, nel lontano Loch Modan. Se hai in programma di dirigerti a nord, potresti consegnargli questo pacco?$b$bL\'ultimo messaggio che ho ricevuto dal Montanaro Piccatonante diceva che si trovava nella torre di guardia settentrionale di Loch Modan.',objectives_loc9='Consegna il Pacco per Piccatonante al Montanaro Piccatonante nella regione di Loch Modan.' WHERE entry=353; /* title: Stormpike\'s Delivery */ /* details: The Stormpikes are a respected dwarven clan, and are well known for their fine and discerning tastes.  So it\'s no wonder that Gringer Stormpike, a Mountaineer of Ironforge, commissioned me to craft him a weapon.$B$BThe weapon is finished, but... Mountaineer Stormpike is far away, in distant Loch Modan.  If you plan on traveling to the north, can you deliver this package to him?$B$BMy last message from Mountaineer Stormpike said he\'s stationed at the northern guard tower in Loch Modan. */ /* objectives: Deliver the Package for Stormpike to Mountaineer Stormpike in Loch Modan. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Deaths in the Family',details_loc9='The Agamand family was the most prosperous family in Tirisfal Glades.  I used to work their mills...before the Plague.$b$bWhen the Scourge first came, the Agamands fortified their home and convinced those in their employ to remain and help them defend.  We were fools, but at least we were loyal fools.$b$bThe Agamands, in their pride, doomed us to undeath.  And now they are minions of the Scourge!$b$bServe the Forsaken by defeating the Agamands who fell to the Plague.  Serve me by bringing me their remains.' WHERE entry=354; /* title: Deaths in the Family */ /* details: The Agamand family was the most prosperous family in Tirisfal Glades.  I used to work their mills...before the Plague.$B$BWhen the Scourge first came, the Agamands fortified their home and convinced those in their employ to remain and help them defend.  We were fools, but at least we were loyal fools.$B$BThe Agamands, in their pride, doomed us to undeath.  And now they are minions of the Scourge!$B$BServe the Forsaken by defeating the Agamands who fell to the Plague.  Serve me by bringing me their remains. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Speak with Sevren',details_loc9='You have given me the remains of the Agamands, and satisfied my desire for revenge.  But the Agamand Mills hold a threat to all the Forsaken, not just to me.$b$bI have spoken to Magistrate Sevren of your exploits against the Agamands, and he wishes to speak with you.' WHERE entry=355; /* title: Speak with Sevren */ /* details: You have given me the remains of the Agamands, and satisfied my desire for revenge.  But the Agamand Mills hold a threat to all the Forsaken, not just to me.$B$BI have spoken to Magistrate Sevren of your exploits against the Agamands, and he wishes to speak with you. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Rear Guard Patrol' WHERE entry=356; /* title: Rear Guard Patrol */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='The Lich\'s Identity' WHERE entry=357; /* title: The Lich\'s Identity */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Graverobbers' WHERE entry=358; /* title: Graverobbers */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='Forsaken Duties',details_loc9='Ho bisogno di notizie fresche dalla nostra postazione dei Guardiamorte a est.$b$bDevo sapere se altre forze del Flagello hanno superato la Granbarricata e sono entrate a Tirisfal. Dobbiamo tenere gli occhi aperti sul confine delle Terre Infette. Non possiamo permettere che il Flagello rinforzi la sua posizione qui!$b$bPercorri la strada verso sud, poi al bivio vai a est verso la postazione. Parla con la Guardiamorte Linnea, lei ha le informazioni di cui ho bisogno.' WHERE entry=359; /* title: Forsaken Duties */ /* details: I need a fresh report from our Deathguard waystation to the east.$B$BI must know if more Scourge forces have slipped past The Bulwark and into Tirisfal.  Our vigilance on the border to the Plaguelands must be maintained - we can\'t let the Scourge get a stronger foothold here!$B$BTravel south along the road, then east at the fork to the waystation.  Speak with Deathguard Linnea.  She has the information I need. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc9='A Letter Undelivered' WHERE entry=361; /* title: A Letter Undelivered */
UPDATE locales_quest SET RequestItemsText_loc9='Si?' WHERE entry=361; /* RequestItemsText: Yes? */
